Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.55,0:54:25.70,Artifact,,0,0,0,,去介绍该音乐股份公司的新走向\N{\fs30}to outline the music group's new direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.95,0:54:27.74,Artifact,,0,0,0,,其员工得到内部消息\N{\fs30}Inside staff learned that EMI is set
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.74,0:54:29.78,Artifact,,0,0,0,,EMI打算裁员2000人\N{\fs30}to axe up to 2000 jobs.
