Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.51,0:54:35.99,Artifact,,0,0,0,,他们让一些对唱片界 或音乐界\N{\fs30}They put people in charge that never had any experience
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.99,0:54:39.57,Artifact,,0,0,0,,一无所知的人来管理\N{\fs30}in the record business or the music business.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.57,0:54:41.50,Artifact,,0,0,0,,他们开始把公司分散开来\N{\fs30}They started to decentralize it.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.50,0:54:43.02,Artifact,,0,0,0,,建立了这些奇怪的单元制\N{\fs30}They had all this strange pods
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.02,0:54:44.90,Artifact,,0,0,0,,打破了原先比较传统的结构\N{\fs30}instead of a more traditional structure.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.90,0:54:47.96,Artifact,,0,0,0,,他们还把重要的权力职位\N{\fs30}They also put some people in positions of power
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.96,0:54:50.32,Artifact,,0,0,0,,给了一些我认为完全不靠谱的人\N{\fs30}who didn't make any sense to me whatsoever.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.45,0:54:52.45,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我一直旁观着\N{\fs30}I see it all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.45,0:54:54.84,Artifact,,0,0,0,,就是这些要大力改革的人\N{\fs30}It is just the heavy hand of guys,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.84,0:54:56.36,Artifact,,0,0,0,,他们不懂这个产业\N{\fs30}who don't understand the business,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.36,0:54:58.18,Artifact,,0,0,0,,却努力要告诉那些懂行的人\N{\fs30}who try to tell people who do understand the business
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.18,0:54:59.17,Artifact,,0,0,0,,应该怎么做\N{\fs30}how to do their jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.84,0:55:01.28,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我见过他一面 他跟我说:\N{\fs30}I met with him once and he said to me:
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.28,0:55:03.32,Artifact,,0,0,0,,"你们这些做音乐业的人,\N{\fs30}"All you people from the music business.
