Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.59,0:55:14.36,Artifact,,0,0,0,,而原有的正经做唱片公司的主管\N{\fs30}And these serious record company executives
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.36,0:55:16.32,Artifact,,0,0,0,,在几个月内就全消失了\N{\fs30}were gone instead in a matter of month.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.68,0:55:18.52,Artifact,,0,0,0,,显然 我有些成见\N{\fs30}Obviously, I have a certain bias
