Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.95,0:55:49.53,Artifact,,0,0,0,,再也不是当初那个公司 和那批人了\N{\fs30}It's not the company or the people it ever was.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.53,0:55:52.71,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我们经历过EMI公司的很多次重组\N{\fs30}We have been through so many regimes at EMI
