Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.81,0:57:23.16,Artifact,,0,0,0,,他本来要做什么\N{\fs30}that he was gonna do something
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.16,0:57:24.52,Artifact,,0,0,0,,但又不做了?\N{\fs30}and then not do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.20,0:57:40.53,Artifact,,0,0,0,,大洋彼岸 是Guy Hands\N{\fs30}Across the pond, it's Guy Hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.31,0:57:44.64,Artifact,,0,0,0,,而在咱美国 是Jeff Kempler(美国维珍唱片首席财务官)\N{\fs30}and here in America, it's Jeff Kempler.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.64,0:57:46.88,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我认为他可能是在朝Guy Hands炫耀\N{\fs30}And I think that he is either trying to show off for Guy Hands
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.32,0:57:49.26,Artifact,,0,0,0,,他认为他能扼制这一切\N{\fs30}and he thinks that he's gonna strangle all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.86,0:57:50.96,Artifact,,0,0,0,,但我们有别的选择\N{\fs30}We have other options.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.96,0:57:54.05,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我 我自己是要奉陪到底的\N{\fs30}I, myself I'm ready to go all the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.69,0:57:56.96,Artifact,,0,0,0,,他们一副准备好的样子 很乐意\N{\fs30}They're acting like they're so ready and happy
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.96,0:57:59.10,Artifact,,0,0,0,,并且愿意与我们当庭对峙\N{\fs30}and willing to just go into litigation
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.10,0:58:02.15,Artifact,,0,0,0,,这样我就必须得准备作战方案了\N{\fs30}that I'm having to prepare the battle plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.75,0:58:06.35,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我想这个合约涉及的所有人 都逐渐迷失了\N{\fs30}I think everyone is getting lost in the deal
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.35,0:58:09.59,Artifact,,0,0,0,,看不到这样对他们\N{\fs30}and not seeing what a benefit
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.59,0:58:12.19,Artifact,,0,0,0,,对我 能有什么好处\N{\fs30}it probably could be to me and to them,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.19,0:58:14.35,Artifact,,0,0,0,,对我们来说 是想达成一项公平合理的协议\N{\fs30}for us to work out something fair and reasonable.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.35,0:58:17.26,Artifact,,0,0,0,,但我不能 我就是不能啊\N{\fs30}But I can't do, I just can't do it
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.26,0:58:19.10,Artifact,,0,0,0,,要是不公平\N{\fs30}if it's not fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.10,0:58:21.33,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我不能一边同意 一边感到自己吃了亏\N{\fs30}I can't do it and feel I've been taking advantage of.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.33,0:58:23.19,Artifact,,0,0,0,,好了 那下一步是什么\N{\fs30}Okay, so what's the next move here?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.03,0:58:32.58,Artifact,,0,0,0,,怎么?\N{\fs30}What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.78,0:58:34.49,Artifact,,0,0,0,,再过来一下   -好的\N{\fs30}We need you again... (Okay)
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.62,0:58:38.31,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我以为那首歌会挺容易的\N{\fs30}I thought that was gonna be an easy song.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.42,0:58:40.05,Artifact,,0,0,0,,-嗯  -我不觉得\N{\fs30}(yeah) I actually didn't think
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.05,0:58:40.99,Artifact,,0,0,0,,这首歌简单\N{\fs30}it was gonna be an easy song,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.99,0:58:42.84,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我就知道这首得特么蛋疼死\N{\fs30}I knew it's gonna be a pain in the fucking ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.26,0:58:48.82,Artifact,,0,0,0,,呃 咱们能不能试试... 呃 你懂的\N{\fs30}Em. Can we try... Em. Just... You know?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.02,0:58:53.91,Artifact,,0,0,0,,当然... 就是... 快一点\N{\fs30}Sure... It's huh... Pretty fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.78,0:59:03.63,Artifact,,0,0,0,,一拍好 还是两拍好?\N{\fs30}Is it better one foot or two?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.63,0:59:04.83,Artifact,,0,0,0,,一拍吧\N{\fs30}One, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.90,0:59:09.25,Artifact,,0,0,0,,真奇怪 这么快\N{\fs30}It's so weird, it's so fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.12,0:59:10.87,Artifact,,0,0,0,,真麻烦\N{\fs30}It's very awkward.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.30,0:59:15.30,Artifact,,0,0,0,,上帝啊\N{\fs30}Jesus Christ!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.54,0:59:17.69,Artifact,,0,0,0,,你到底想要什么 哥们\N{\fs30}You know what you want, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.90,0:59:19.08,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我要力量 力量\N{\fs30}I need power... Need power...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.36,0:59:20.33,Artifact,,0,0,0,,一拍不够\N{\fs30}It's not enough at one.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.83,0:59:24.68,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我会了兄弟 我亲弟弟 对吧?\N{\fs30}I got it brother, my brother. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.57,0:59:32.57,Artifact,,0,0,0,,一会儿再弄\N{\fs30}We will work with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.67,0:59:33.82,Artifact,,0,0,0,,过一会儿叫你\N{\fs30}We'll call you in a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.40,0:59:36.31,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fs30}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.30,0:59:38.97,Artifact,,0,0,0,,完全迷茫\N{\fs30}I have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.97,0:59:43.15,Artifact,,0,0,0,,速度上太不连续了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.15,0:59:45.65,Artifact,,0,0,0,,节奏上时快时慢
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.90,0:59:47.36,Artifact,,0,0,0,,是 我也是人 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:59:47.49,0:59:49.91,Artifact,,0,0,0,,所以我想让你...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.91,0:59:51.07,Artifact,,0,0,0,,这样就更流畅起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.07,0:59:52.91,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我是说 实际上...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.91,0:59:54.08,Artifact,,0,0,0,,你都还没练呢    -对
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.08,0:59:56.75,Artifact,,0,0,0,,你要是练上个几天 我肯定你就能行了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.50,0:59:58.08,Artifact,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.08,1:00:00.12,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我们可能得先做下一首歌了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.12,1:00:02.17,Artifact,,0,0,0,,留时间给你每天练一练这个
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.17,1:00:04.75,Artifact,,0,0,0,,然后过个两三周我们再回来做这首
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.75,1:00:06.17,Artifact,,0,0,0,,因为现在真是太不流畅
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.97,1:00:09.34,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我已经做到最好了 哥们
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.46,1:00:11.84,Artifact,,0,0,0,,那就想个更好的鼓点啊 我们必须要录这首歌
Dialogue: 0,1:00:11.84,1:00:12.26,Artifact,,0,0,0,,就这个鼓点了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.26,1:00:13.89,Artifact,,0,0,0,,要么咱干脆抛弃这首歌 要么咱就尽量...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.89,1:00:14.72,Artifact,,0,0,0,,就这个鼓点 哥们
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.56,1:00:16.68,Artifact,,0,0,0,,你想要我怎样？
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.72,1:00:19.10,Artifact,,0,0,0,,现在这样我没法唱
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.14,1:00:21.52,Artifact,,0,0,0,,你给我再多的钱
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.60,1:00:23.19,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我也没法正确地唱出来
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.19,1:00:23.86,Artifact,,0,0,0,,这样不行
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.99,1:00:31.15,Artifact,,0,0,0,,你能打开喇叭放一下吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.73,1:00:33.19,Artifact,,0,0,0,,你看这样一点怎么样:\N{\fs30}What about a little bit of like:
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.89,1:00:51.78,Artifact,,0,0,0,,有时候你觉得充满力量\N{\fs30}Some days you feel so strong
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.78,1:00:53.56,Artifact,,0,0,0,,然后 其他时候 你就觉得:\N{\fs30}and then, other days, you're like:
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.56,1:00:54.96,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我他妈在干嘛啊\N{\fs30}what the fuck am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.88,1:00:57.46,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我想 我是不是正在毁掉一切?\N{\fs30}I'm wondering if I'm ruining it?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.21,1:01:00.15,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我是不是正在毁掉Shannon和Tomo?\N{\fs30}Am I fucking it all up for Shannon and Tomo?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.78,1:01:02.64,Artifact,,0,0,0,,有时候我感到好自信 好强势\N{\fs30}Some days, I feel so confident, so strong,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.64,1:01:05.35,Artifact,,0,0,0,,就像: 没关系的\N{\fs30}I'm like: it doesn't matter
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.35,1:01:06.79,Artifact,,0,0,0,,这张专辑肯定会特别的好\N{\fs30}this album is gonna be so good,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.26,1:01:10.26,Artifact,,0,0,0,,歌曲肯定超级棒\N{\fs30}the songs are gonna be so great.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.58,1:01:11.99,Artifact,,0,0,0,,不用在乎我们属于哪家唱片公司\N{\fs30}It doesn't matter what label we are,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.99,1:01:14.60,Artifact,,0,0,0,,人们一定会来听我们的歌 我们只是需要协助\N{\fs30}we're gonna reach people but you need the help.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.60,1:01:16.47,Artifact,,0,0,0,,你需要... 你不可能所有的事都自己做\N{\fs30}You need... You can't do it on your own.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.81,1:01:18.27,Artifact,,0,0,0,,而别的时候 我就在想:\N{\fs30}And the other days, you just feel like:
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.27,1:01:19.51,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我们他妈的是在干嘛啊?\N{\fs30}what the fuck are we doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:19.83,1:01:20.69,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我也不知道\N{\fs30}And I don't know,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.69,1:01:22.48,Artifact,,0,0,0,,也许我就不该这么斗争\N{\fs30}maybe I'm fucked up to keep fighting.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.48,1:01:24.98,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我只出过一张成功的专辑\N{\fs30}I've had one successful record.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.31,1:01:28.18,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我就争得像...\N{\fs30}And I'm fighting like,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.18,1:01:29.98,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我是他妈的滚石乐队一样\N{\fs30}I am the Rolling fucking Stones.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.28,1:01:31.66,Artifact,,0,0,0,,可我算个屁啊?\N{\fs30}I mean who the fuck am I?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.19,1:01:33.50,Artifact,,0,0,0,,真是他妈噩梦哥们\N{\fs30}It's a fucking nightmare, man,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.50,1:01:36.29,Artifact,,0,0,0,,整个事都是个他妈的噩梦\N{\fs30}this whole thing is a fucking nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.67,1:01:41.19,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我是说 这一切过一年后就有可能...\N{\fs30}I mean, all of this could be a year from now,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.19,1:01:45.18,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我是说 到时回头一看 说: "哇 我搞砸了!"\N{\fs30}I mean, looking back and say: "Wow, I fucked up!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.58,1:01:46.82,Artifact,,0,0,0,,"我没签唱片公司,\N{\fs30}I didn't sign with the label,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.16,1:01:48.92,Artifact,,0,0,0,,"专辑才他妈卖了12张"\N{\fs30}the record sold 12 fucking copies."
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.98,1:01:53.17,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我把所有的一切都投入这里面\N{\fs30}I put everything that I have into this.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.97,1:01:57.11,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我的全部身家 一切 我们都是\N{\fs30}My entire life, everything. We all have.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.29,1:02:14.54,地名,,0,0,0,,{\pos(295,440)}诉讼第112天
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.73,1:02:15.53,Artifact,,0,0,0,,你还是别走这些\N{\fs30}You don't want to get through
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.53,1:02:16.81,Artifact,,0,0,0,,所有的诉讼程序了\N{\fs30}all this fucking legal thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.81,1:02:18.78,Artifact,,0,0,0,,你也赢不了什么\N{\fs30}And you don't win anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.78,1:02:19.85,Artifact,,0,0,0,,如果这是彩虹尽头的\N{\fs30}If it was like a pot of gold
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.85,1:02:21.09,Artifact,,0,0,0,,一滩金矿 我就去了\N{\fs30}at the end of that rainbow, I'll do it...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.09,1:02:23.45,Artifact,,0,0,0,,你的赢头就是: 你什么也不失去\N{\fs30}The win is: you don't lose anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.45,1:02:24.67,Artifact,,0,0,0,,明白吧 那还是赢的!\N{\fs30}Hey, that's your win!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.67,1:02:26.67,Artifact,,0,0,0,,你赢 就是 诉讼费用你来付\N{\fs30}The win is that you get to pay the legal fees.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.67,1:02:27.44,Artifact,,0,0,0,,那就是你的赢头\N{\fs30}That's what your win is.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:27.44,1:02:28.88,Artifact,,0,0,0,,赢就是这样...\N{\fs30}That's the win...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:29.25,1:02:30.21,Artifact,,0,0,0,,看你们有点沮丧\N{\fs30}You look to have some fun.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.21,1:02:31.81,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我跟Kempler半年没说话了(EMI/维京首席财务官)\N{\fs30}I haven't talked to Kempler in 6 months.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.81,1:02:33.54,Artifact,,0,0,0,,咱给他打个电话 你们的官司...\N{\fs30}Let's call him. Your lawsuit...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.54,1:02:36.54,Artifact,,0,0,0,,嘿Brenna! 给Jeff Kempler打电话\N{\fs30}Hey! Brenna, call Jeff Kempler.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:37.10,1:02:38.95,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我可能不会太客气 说真的\N{\fs30}I'm gonna have trouble being nice, seriously...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.45,1:02:41.56,Artifact,,0,0,0,,嘿 我在机场的洗手间呢\N{\fs30}Hey guys, I'm in the bathroom at the airport,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.56,1:02:42.50,Artifact,,0,0,0,,所以这儿有点吵\N{\fs30}so it's a little loud.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.79,1:02:44.72,Artifact,,0,0,0,,可能也有点冷吧\N{\fs30}It's probably a little cold, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.70,1:02:46.74,Artifact,,0,0,0,,好冷啊 怎么能这么冷
Dialogue: 0,1:02:46.70,1:02:49.32,Artifact,,0,0,0,,你冻病了我才高兴呢\N{\fs30}Any place where it's cold for you makes me happy
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.32,1:02:50.40,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我是Irving\N{\fs30}It's Irving.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:50.27,1:02:53.54,Artifact,,0,0,0,,噢哥们 我能让你开心 我真是受宠若惊
Dialogue: 0,1:02:53.54,1:02:58.30,Artifact,,0,0,0,,再让你高兴点: 我现在感觉可烦了呢
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.09,1:03:01.46,Artifact,,0,0,0,,趁我手机还没被没收 我先说几句
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.51,1:03:03.97,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我是说 你知道我们也在努力 是吧
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.97,1:03:06.59,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我打了很多电话 尝试了很多方案
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.93,1:03:09.64,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我们真的在努力 我们也很想跟你们...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.64,1:03:10.93,Artifact,,0,0,0,,回到谈判桌上来...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.15,1:03:13.14,Artifact,,0,0,0,,你听起来像个冠冕堂皇的混蛋\N{\fs30}You sound like a corporate fucking dick,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.14,1:03:14.48,Artifact,,0,0,0,,咱们还是说合同吧\N{\fs30}let's just talk about the deal.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.92,1:03:16.48,Artifact,,0,0,0,,事实就是 你懂的\N{\fs30}The reality of fact is that: it's, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.48,1:03:19.46,Artifact,,0,0,0,,很难说服这些人(30STM)\N{\fs30}it's really hard to advise these guys
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.46,1:03:22.15,Artifact,,0,0,0,,跟你们这个垃圾破公司\N{\fs30}to do anything with that piece of shit of a company
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.15,1:03:26.23,Artifact,,0,0,0,,达成什么协约 说对 说不 滚吧你\N{\fs30}that you work for, and say yes, say no, go away man,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.23,1:03:28.41,Artifact,,0,0,0,,没什么话说  就滚吧\N{\fs30}just go away, if you don't want to do this.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.41,1:03:30.32,Artifact,,0,0,0,,还有在他们从你们手底下\N{\fs30}And before they fucking sell the company out
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.32,1:03:31.92,Artifact,,0,0,0,,卖空这破公司之前 把专辑发了\N{\fs30}from under you guys, put out the record.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.92,1:03:32.54,Artifact,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs30}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.54,1:03:34.49,Artifact,,0,0,0,,不过还是旅途平安啊 再见\N{\fs30}But fly safe anyway. Bye.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.49,1:03:37.96,Artifact,,0,0,0,,对了 还有些次要问题   -对\N{\fs30}Right. By the way just side issue.   -Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.38,1:03:39.51,Artifact,,0,0,0,,唱片公司怎么样了?\N{\fs30}How is the record company?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.57,1:03:47.05,Artifact,,0,0,0,,咋了?\N{\fs30}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.05,1:03:48.07,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我就想感觉好点\N{\fs30}I just want to feel good.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.07,1:03:49.43,Artifact,,0,0,0,,整个的谈判 感觉都不好\N{\fs30}This all negotiations, it doesn't feel good.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:49.43,1:03:51.27,Artifact,,0,0,0,,就不该感觉好\N{\fs30}It's not supposed to feel good.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.27,1:03:51.75,Artifact,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs30}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.76,1:03:53.52,Artifact,,0,0,0,,整个这个事 面对 动荡的时间\N{\fs30}This whole thing. You've got the unstable time.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.52,1:03:55.72,Artifact,,0,0,0,,还有 动荡的EMI\N{\fs30}You've got the unstable EMI.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:55.72,1:03:57.77,Artifact,,0,0,0,,一切都像 脱缰的野马一样\N{\fs30}You've got the unstable maverick way.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.77,1:03:59.44,Artifact,,0,0,0,,这事...充满了动荡\N{\fs30}The thing... It's all unstable.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.44,1:04:02.14,Artifact,,0,0,0,,所以完全没有(确定下来的)感觉\N{\fs30}So, there's no feeling that's gonna be attached,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:02.14,1:04:03.47,Artifact,,0,0,0,,像是"噢 好了..."\N{\fs30}to like: "Oh! Yeah..."
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.47,1:04:04.69,Artifact,,0,0,0,,然后还有新专辑要做\N{\fs30}Then you've got the album we're doing
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.69,1:04:05.86,Artifact,,0,0,0,,还有一切的这些事\N{\fs30}and you've got everything, dude.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.86,1:04:07.44,Artifact,,0,0,0,,有点动荡 你懂的\N{\fs30}It's a little unstable, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.79,1:04:10.69,Artifact,,0,0,0,,站出来的经理们\N{\fs30}Managers who are standing up
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.69,1:04:12.09,Artifact,,0,0,0,,都表示他们十分忧虑\N{\fs30}and say they are very very worried
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.09,1:04:14.06,Artifact,,0,0,0,,EMI存在的动荡\N{\fs30}about the instability at EMI.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.27,1:04:15.74,Artifact,,0,0,0,,知名艺人 如电台司令乐队\N{\fs30}Major acts like Radiohead and
Dialogue: 0,1:04:15.74,1:04:18.18,Artifact,,0,0,0,,和保罗·麦卡特尼 都与该公司分道扬镳\N{\fs30}Paul McCartney parted ways with the company.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:18.18,1:04:19.21,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我刚跟我的制作人说了,\N{\fs30}And I just said to my producers,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.21,1:04:20.75,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我说我发这张专辑\N{\fs30}I said I want to feel excited
Dialogue: 0,1:04:21.27,1:04:22.28,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我想感到点兴奋\N{\fs30}by releasing this record.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.46,1:04:26.17,网页,,0,0,0,,{\c&H87674A&\pos(100,474)}麦卡特尼称其唱片公司“无聊”
Dialogue: 0,1:04:26.51,1:04:27.42,Artifact,,0,0,0,,太乱了\N{\fs30}It's just a mess.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:28.05,1:04:29.23,Artifact,,0,0,0,,他们想操纵我们\N{\fs30}They're trying to manipulate us
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.23,1:04:30.28,Artifact,,0,0,0,,让我们恐惧\N{\fs30}with a little bit of fear.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.53,1:04:32.17,Artifact,,0,0,0,,他们从我们眼皮底下撤掉合约\N{\fs30}They're pulling deals out from under our feet,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.17,1:04:34.29,Artifact,,0,0,0,,他们在耍我们 在糊弄我们\N{\fs30}they're fucking with us, they're toying,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.29,1:04:36.41,Artifact,,0,0,0,,他们在发邮件 发信\N{\fs30}they're sending eMails, letters
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.41,1:04:37.97,Artifact,,0,0,0,,完全与我们对立\N{\fs30}just outright hostile.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.21,1:04:40.77,Artifact,,0,0,0,,据报道 EMI的动荡 令Coldplay\N{\fs30}The shakeup at EMI reportedly has Coldplay
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.77,1:04:42.71,Artifact,,0,0,0,,正重新考虑将来续约的事\N{\fs30}rethinking a future deal with the label.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:42.93,1:04:45.11,Artifact,,0,0,0,,罗比·威廉姆斯的经理人声称:\N{\fs30}Robbie Williams's manager has been quoted as saying:
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.11,1:04:47.77,Artifact,,0,0,0,,"该明星现在不急于发放新专辑\N{\fs30}"The star is in no rush to put out a new album
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.82,1:04:51.36,网页,,0,0,0,,{\pos(806,276)}电台司令乐队退出\N 罗比·威廉姆斯罢工\N -至今已裁员1000人
Dialogue: 0,1:04:47.77,1:04:49.66,Artifact,,0,0,0,,"因为对新的管理模式缺乏信心"\N{\fs30}due to a lack of faith in the new management."
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.50,1:04:53.18,Artifact,,0,0,0,,今天是Guy Hands向其债权人之一的\N{\fs30}Today marks the deadline for Hands
Dialogue: 0,1:04:53.18,1:04:56.41,Artifact,,0,0,0,,花旗集团支付款项的最后期限\N{\fs30}to meet a payment to Citigroup, one of its creditors,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.41,1:04:57.70,Artifact,,0,0,0,,不然他将失去对公司的掌控\N{\fs30}or he'll lose control of the firm.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.35,1:05:01.08,Artifact,,0,0,0,,这些人都是 说一套做一套的人\N{\fs30}These people that they say one thing and that they do another thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.08,1:05:04.20,Artifact,,0,0,0,,他们这样做生意 真是恶心\N{\fs30}It's disgusting that they do business like this.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.20,1:05:06.73,Artifact,,0,0,0,,他们怪不得自己名声这么臭\N{\fs30}They wonder why they have a bad fucking name.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.32,1:05:09.76,Artifact,,0,0,0,,因为他们对人就像屎一样\N{\fs30}It's because they treat people like fucking shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.76,1:05:14.70,Artifact,,0,0,0,,妈的他们活该遭现在这个灾\N{\fs30}They deserve the fucking disaster that they are in the middle of.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:17.97,1:05:19.31,Artifact,,0,0,0,,出去走走 不然我该砸东西了\N{\fs30}Walking out before I break shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.75,1:05:21.11,Artifact,,0,0,0,,你懂的 这你得教教我了\N{\fs30}You know you've got to guide me here,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.11,1:05:22.99,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我脑子里一团乱麻 不知道该怎么做\N{\fs30}I'm heel over my head, I don't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.64,1:05:24.65,Artifact,,0,0,0,,呃 我也不知道\N{\fs30}Huh, I don't know either.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.18,1:05:27.54,Artifact,,0,0,0,,这个傻逼诉讼就这么占领了我们的生活\N{\fs30}It's amazing how this fucked-up-lawsuit
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.54,1:05:29.04,Artifact,,0,0,0,,真是没法想象\N{\fs30}is taking over our lives.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.84,1:05:31.26,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我觉得我们应该签\N{\fs30}I feel like fuck we should just take
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.26,1:05:33.30,Artifact,,0,0,0,,那个要死的合约 不管是什么\N{\fs30}the god damn deal, whatever it is
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.30,1:05:34.17,Artifact,,0,0,0,,就他妈签了吧\N{\fs30}just fucking take it,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:34.17,1:05:35.61,Artifact,,0,0,0,,万一出更坏的事呢?\N{\fs30}what if everything got worse?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.60,1:05:51.35,Artifact,,0,0,0,,这一部分 真是专辑里我最\N{\fs30}This part of the record is always really
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.35,1:05:53.46,Artifact,,0,0,0,,最最最看中的\N{\fs30}really really important for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:53.77,1:05:55.40,Artifact,,0,0,0,,好像那里的背景伴奏\N{\fs30}It's like the backing tracks are there,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.91,1:05:58.11,Artifact,,0,0,0,,有强烈的个性\N{\fs30}they've got a lot of strong personality.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.11,1:05:59.84,Artifact,,0,0,0,,不管那是好是坏\N{\fs30}It doesn't matter whether it's good or bad.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:00.23,1:06:01.43,Artifact,,0,0,0,,可以快 可以慢\N{\fs30}It could be fast, it could be slow,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.43,1:06:04.10,Artifact,,0,0,0,,但都有着某种精华在里面\N{\fs30}but they've all got some sort of essence to them
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.10,1:06:05.77,Artifact,,0,0,0,,使歌曲脱颖而出\N{\fs30}that makes the songs stand out.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.47,1:06:08.02,Artifact,,0,0,0,,现在 它像是正在灌入\N{\fs30}And now, it's like filling in,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.58,1:06:09.94,Artifact,,0,0,0,,正在给整个画面上色\N{\fs30}it's coloring the picture.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.88,1:06:12.47,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我觉得就是那个部分\N{\fs30}And I think that's the part
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.47,1:06:15.09,Artifact,,0,0,0,,是你一直所欠缺的\N{\fs30}that has been missing from you.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.56,1:06:18.42,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我得说一句 卧了个大槽!\N{\fs30}I have to say: holy fuck!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.42,1:06:19.41,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我今天的感觉就是这样\N{\fs30}That's how I feel today.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:20.52,1:06:23.49,Artifact,,0,0,0,,没有那种 完 全 碉 堡 的东西\N{\fs30}You don't have like undeniable.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.21,1:06:26.53,Artifact,,0,0,0,,对 咱现在是没有 没错\N{\fs30}No, we don't right now as we speak, No!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.05,1:06:28.64,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我再在这儿坐上一年\N{\fs30}I'll sit here for another year,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:28.64,1:06:30.49,Artifact,,0,0,0,,不行的话 我把这货整个中国特色掉\N{\fs30}I'll Chinese democracy this motherfucker
Dialogue: 0,1:06:30.49,1:06:32.38,Artifact,,0,0,0,,一点问题没有\N{\fs30}if I have to. It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:32.63,1:06:34.50,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我完全明白你的意思\N{\fs30}I know exactly what you're talking about
Dialogue: 0,1:06:34.50,1:06:38.31,Artifact,,0,0,0,,这也是做专辑时的正常阶段\N{\fs30}and this is quite usual at this stage of making a record.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.31,1:06:43.10,Artifact,,0,0,0,,现在这个时期令你怀疑一切\N{\fs30}You're now in the place where you're doubting everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:43.10,1:06:48.70,Artifact,,0,0,0,,一切都走向了某种瓶颈 而且从根本上讲\N{\fs30}Everything is sort of plateauing and fundamentally,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:48.70,1:06:50.78,Artifact,,0,0,0,,没有什么能挑动你们的神经的了\N{\fs30}there is nothing that's getting your juices going.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.35,1:06:53.43,Artifact,,0,0,0,,而我的建议就是\N{\fs30}And what I suggest is
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.43,1:06:55.42,Artifact,,0,0,0,,咱们得从大局着眼\N{\fs30}that we need to look at the whole thing,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.42,1:06:56.62,Artifact,,0,0,0,,因为--\N{\fs30}because...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.62,1:06:57.96,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我们肯定还差一首歌\N{\fs30}We're definitely missing a song
Dialogue: 0,1:06:58.23,1:06:59.52,Artifact,,0,0,0,,这个我能明确告诉你\N{\fs30}I can tell you that right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.61,1:07:00.50,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我同意你说的\N{\fs30}No, I agree with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.59,1:07:03.55,Artifact,,0,0,0,,所以 可以这样\N{\fs30}So, it might be that
Dialogue: 0,1:07:03.55,1:07:05.89,Artifact,,0,0,0,,这个阶段完全可以:\N{\fs30}that has to be a period of just like:
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.14,1:07:08.98,Artifact,,0,0,0,,"好 我们确实缺这个"\N{\fs30}okay, we are missing this,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.98,1:07:10.75,Artifact,,0,0,0,,"我们确实需要再做一首歌"\N{\fs30}we do need to do another song
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.75,1:07:13.06,Artifact,,0,0,0,,但也许它还没写出来\N{\fs30}but maybe it hasn't been written.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.69,1:07:16.50,Artifact,,0,0,0,,但在你们把其他的歌\N{\fs30}But without at least getting
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.50,1:07:17.98,Artifact,,0,0,0,,弄好之前\N{\fs30}some of these other songs into point
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.98,1:07:19.82,Artifact,,0,0,0,,你们找不到你们缺失的东西\N{\fs30}you're not going to know what you're missing.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.33,1:07:22.02,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我希望这是 你懂的\N{\fs30}I hope that this is mid... You know,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.80,1:07:25.80,Artifact,,0,0,0,,是专辑的中年危机\N{\fs30}the midlife crisis of the record,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:26.25,1:07:29.35,Artifact,,0,0,0,,但我不知道 我是说 我们得质疑所有成果\N{\fs30}but I don't know, I mean, we have to question everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.95,1:07:34.95,Artifact,,0,0,0,,在我看来 我觉得这是个很好的学习过程
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.95,1:07:38.87,Artifact,,0,0,0,,对我而言 我觉得这是个很好的学习过程
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.37,1:07:41.41,Artifact,,0,0,0,,学习当你实际上只能自食其力的时候
Dialogue: 0,1:07:41.41,1:07:45.33,Artifact,,0,0,0,,该如何制作唱片
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.33,1:07:49.84,Artifact,,0,0,0,,因为我们没有唱片公司 没有人来管理
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.54,1:07:52.92,Artifact,,0,0,0,,只有我们四个人在房间里
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.71,1:07:56.72,Artifact,,0,0,0,,制作一张三十秒上火星乐队的唱片
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.72,1:07:58.64,Artifact,,0,0,0,,这是个很陌生的情况
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.64,1:08:01.01,Artifact,,0,0,0,,目前也没有任何出路
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.30,1:08:07.22,地名,,0,0,0,,{\pos(682,468)}诉讼第139天\N{\fs46}12月31日
Dialogue: 0,1:08:06.36,1:08:08.35,Artifact,,0,0,0,,现在是早上 凌晨的早上\N{\fs30}It's the morning, early early morning,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:08.35,1:08:09.28,Artifact,,0,0,0,,外面还黑着\N{\fs30}it's still dark out and
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.28,1:08:12.47,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我们决定离开洛杉矶\N{\fs30}we have decided to get out of Los Angeles.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.82,1:08:15.81,Artifact,,0,0,0,,去佛罗里达州\N{\fs30}And go to Florida.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:17.10,1:08:18.96,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我不能接受\N{\fs30}I just couldn't face
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.96,1:08:20.59,Artifact,,0,0,0,,大除夕的什么特么也不做\N{\fs30}not doing something for fucking New Year's Eve.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:21.08,1:08:23.31,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我们这一年都特么在辛苦着\N{\fs30}We've been going at it all fucking year.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:23.70,1:08:24.82,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我这周要跳舞\N{\fs30}I want to dance this week.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.04,1:08:26.64,Artifact,,0,0,0,,你会看见我跳成傻子\N{\fs30}You're gonna see a dancing fool.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:28.75,1:08:29.45,Artifact,,0,0,0,,赞\N{\fs30}Ditto.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.18,1:08:39.08,Artifact,,0,0,0,,去之前我得先吃早饭\N{\fs30}I need breakfast before I face this shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:55.63,1:08:56.70,Artifact,,0,0,0,,每个人都放假去了\N{\fs30}Everybody took a break.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.70,1:08:58.56,Artifact,,0,0,0,,Shannon去了夏威夷\N{\fs30}Shannon went to Hawaii,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.94,1:09:04.55,Artifact,,0,0,0,,Tomo去了密歇根州\N{\fs30}Tomo went to Michigan.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.22,1:09:07.55,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我觉得 空气中弥漫着各种\N{\fs30}I feel like, there's a lot up in the air
Dialogue: 0,1:09:07.55,1:09:10.97,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我还意外发现\N{\fs30}and it was serendipitous
Dialogue: 0,1:09:10.97,1:09:13.43,Artifact,,0,0,0,,这个假期正好处于\N{\fs30}that the holiday break came at the time
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.43,1:09:16.56,Artifact,,0,0,0,,这个我们成败在此一举的节点\N{\fs30}when there was this make-or-break kind of place
Dialogue: 0,1:09:16.56,1:09:18.75,Artifact,,0,0,0,,既是专辑的关键点\N{\fs30}we happen to be in for the record,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:18.75,1:09:21.41,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我们也遇到了创意瓶颈\N{\fs30}for the creative parts of the album,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:21.41,1:09:23.81,Artifact,,0,0,0,,也是官司的关键点\N{\fs30}for the lawsuit.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.06,1:09:27.75,Artifact,,0,0,0,,好没？ 她觉得你是Jared Leto\N{\fs30}Ready? She thinks you are Jared Leto.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:27.95,1:09:28.83,Artifact,,0,0,0,,她让我到这儿来\N{\fs30}She told me to come here
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.83,1:09:30.09,Artifact,,0,0,0,,问问你是不是Jared Leto?\N{\fs30}and ask you if you're Jared Leto?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:30.16,1:09:31.17,Artifact,,0,0,0,,嗯......是啊\N{\fs30}Mmmm. Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.71,1:09:32.50,Artifact,,0,0,0,,你真是? 真心的?\N{\fs30}You are? Serious?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.50,1:09:32.78,Artifact,,0,0,0,,是滴\N{\fs30}Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.78,1:09:34.08,Artifact,,0,0,0,,你耍我们的吧?\N{\fs30}Are you just fucking with us?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:34.29,1:09:36.14,Artifact,,0,0,0,,没...你好吗\N{\fs30}No... How you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.54,1:09:37.98,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我就知道\N{\fs30}I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:37.98,1:09:38.55,Artifact,,0,0,0,,你好吗\N{\fs30}What's up?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.00,1:09:44.38,Artifact,,0,0,0,,你可想不到 "哦这是迈阿密\N{\fs30}You don't think: oh, it's Miami,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:44.38,1:09:45.42,Artifact,,0,0,0,,"会有这么些人"\N{\fs30}there's gonna be all these people
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.42,1:09:46.59,Artifact,,0,0,0,,"在沙滩上围拍你"\N{\fs30}taking pictures on the beach.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:46.99,1:09:48.36,Artifact,,0,0,0,,Michael Jackson!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.36,1:09:49.16,Artifact,,0,0,0,,于是 我们逃走了\N{\fs30}So, we escaped
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.16,1:09:51.05,Artifact,,0,0,0,,去了某个鳄鱼塘之类的地方...\N{\fs30}and went to some alligator farm or something...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.55,1:10:45.61,Artifact,,0,0,0,,真是别有风味 在沼泽里开始新的一年\N{\fs30}There's nothing like starting your new year in a swamp.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:49.15,1:10:51.11,Artifact,,0,0,0,,仅在一月就有60万人失业\N{\fs30}600 000 jobs lost in January.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:51.56,1:10:53.97,Artifact,,0,0,0,,道指已经跌破2000点\N{\fs30}The DOW is already down 2000 points.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:03.01,1:11:05.93,地名,,0,0,0,,{\pos(628,234)}洛杉矶
Dialogue: 0,1:11:09.10,1:11:10.61,Artifact,,0,0,0,,这可是弗兰克·劳埃德·赖特设计的房子\N{\fs30}This is the Frank Lloyd Wright house.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:08.97,1:11:10.70,注释,,0,0,0,,（注：美国著名建筑设计师）
Dialogue: 0,1:11:10.83,1:11:12.37,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我觉得这是个咱们录音的好地方\N{\fs30}I thought that would be a great place for us
Dialogue: 0,1:11:12.37,1:11:14.86,Artifact,,0,0,0,,肯定灵感爆棚\N{\fs30}to record and would be really inspiring.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:29.09,1:11:30.13,Artifact,,0,0,0,,你知道吗 刺激的就是\N{\fs30}You know what's exciting,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:30.21,1:11:32.68,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我们要把这座房子的灵魂录进专辑里\N{\fs30}we're gonna have the spirit of this house inside the record.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.95,1:11:34.85,Artifact,,0,0,0,,这真是个活生生的艺术品啊\N{\fs30}This is a living, breathing piece of art.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:40.69,1:11:42.73,Artifact,,0,0,0,,这儿可真棒
Dialogue: 0,1:12:45.60,1:12:49.93,Artifact,,0,0,0,,艺术 正是我们在作品中一向所追求的\N{\fs30}Art, it's something we all aspire our work to be.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.34,1:12:52.09,Artifact,,0,0,0,,有的人可以想到什么就做什么\N{\fs30}Some people can do whatever they think of.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.37,1:12:55.71,注次级人名,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1060,694)}音乐制作人
Dialogue: 0,1:12:52.40,1:12:53.99,Artifact,,0,0,0,,而他们所想到的十分特别\N{\fs30}And what they think of is special
Dialogue: 0,1:12:54.37,1:12:57.07,Artifact,,0,0,0,,并能感染他人 这样的人就是艺术家\N{\fs30}and moves other people. Those people are artists.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.47,1:13:03.72,Artifact,,0,0,0,,这是他们对于所爱事物的\N{\fs30}It's their bare honest truth
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.97,1:13:04.35,注次级人名,,0,0,0,,{\pos(68,696)}演员
Dialogue: 0,1:13:04.82,1:13:06.55,Artifact,,0,0,0,,最真实的表达\N{\fs30}about something that they love.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.13,1:13:12.36,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我认为这是一种\N{\fs30}I think it's one of the avenues
Dialogue: 0,1:13:12.36,1:13:15.77,Artifact,,0,0,0,,深及内心 探寻自我的途径\N{\fs30}to get to oneself to find out who we are.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:23.24,1:13:25.50,Artifact,,0,0,0,,经久不衰的艺术 是最难的艺术形式\N{\fs30}Timeless art is the most difficult form of art.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:26.15,1:13:27.87,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我看到克莱斯勒大厦\N{\fs30}I see it in the Chrysler building,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:28.65,1:13:30.50,Artifact,,0,0,0,,看到协和式超音速飞机\N{\fs30}I see it in the Concorde.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.50,1:13:33.28,Artifact,,0,0,0,,听到甲壳虫乐队...(都是永恒的艺术品)\N{\fs30}I hear it in the Beatles...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:45.90,1:13:48.67,Artifact,,0,0,0,,这个行业就是: 我恨这帮人\N{\fs30}The business is, I hate all those people,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:48.67,1:13:49.85,Artifact,,0,0,0,,这帮人都是吸血蝙蝠\N{\fs30}those people are leeches.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:50.41,1:13:54.79,Artifact,,0,0,0,,他们只关心自己的饭碗\N{\fs30}All they ever do is care about not losing their job.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:54.79,1:13:59.34,Artifact,,0,0,0,,他们从不关心艺术的价值体现\N{\fs30}They never once care about enhancing the value of art.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:59.98,1:14:02.37,Artifact,,0,0,0,,现今我们行业整体的一大弊病\N{\fs30}One of the problems we have in business at large right now
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.37,1:14:04.72,Artifact,,0,0,0,,就是商业集团在掌管这些生意\N{\fs30}is corporations own these businesses.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:04.72,1:14:07.26,Artifact,,0,0,0,,所以 永远都很难改变\N{\fs30}So, it's very difficult to change it ever
Dialogue: 0,1:14:07.26,1:14:10.36,Artifact,,0,0,0,,因为它必须靠着这个机制来运转\N{\fs30}because it has to be this machine that keeps going.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:10.81,1:14:12.71,Artifact,,0,0,0,,另一方面的问题就是\N{\fs30}The other part of the problem is that
Dialogue: 0,1:14:12.71,1:14:16.28,Artifact,,0,0,0,,行业本身把制作过程同化了\N{\fs30}the business itself has homogenized the process.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:16.56,1:14:18.68,Artifact,,0,0,0,,唱片公司来告诉乐队写什么\N{\fs30}The record company tells a band what to write,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:18.68,1:14:20.45,Artifact,,0,0,0,,如何写 跟谁合作写\N{\fs30}how to write it, who to write with.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:20.45,1:14:21.94,Artifact,,0,0,0,,你知道 把哪首作为单曲\N{\fs30}You know. What is gonna be a single,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:21.94,1:14:23.16,Artifact,,0,0,0,,哪首不作为单曲\N{\fs30}what's not gonna be a single.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:23.22,1:14:27.77,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我认为这样对创意层面的管控太严重了\N{\fs30}And I think has far too much control on a creative level.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:28.11,1:14:31.24,Artifact,,0,0,0,,这样 一切都逐渐变得十分雷同\N{\fs30}So, that everything starts sounding very much the same.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:31.24,1:14:32.28,Artifact,,0,0,0,,这就像个钟摆一样\N{\fs30}That's a pendulum. I think.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:32.28,1:14:33.82,Artifact,,0,0,0,,不可避免地,\N{\fs30}What inevitably happens is
Dialogue: 0,1:14:33.82,1:14:34.99,Artifact,,0,0,0,,公司们总在与艺人抗衡\N{\fs30}that companies that are wrestling with that
Dialogue: 0,1:14:34.99,1:14:37.53,Artifact,,0,0,0,,在创意, 感性  与融合科学之间\N{\fs30}creative, intuitive, blended with science,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.34,1:14:39.85,Artifact,,0,0,0,,他们往理性的方向摆的太远\N{\fs30}they swing way too far to the
Dialogue: 0,1:14:39.85,1:14:42.55,Artifact,,0,0,0,,"让我们遵从科技和数据测算"\N{\fs30}lets-be-scientific-and-mathematical.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:43.18,1:14:44.68,Artifact,,0,0,0,,像是把西瓜和芝麻一起丢了\N{\fs30}Sort of throw the baby out with the bath water
Dialogue: 0,1:14:44.68,1:14:48.50,Artifact,,0,0,0,,然后就失去了对灵感\N{\fs30}and lose that comfort with intuition,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:48.50,1:14:50.17,Artifact,,0,0,0,,创意敏感\N{\fs30}creative sensitivities
Dialogue: 0,1:14:50.17,1:14:52.09,Artifact,,0,0,0,,以及犯错误的信心\N{\fs30}and mistakes get made that way.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:52.09,1:14:53.88,Artifact,,0,0,0,,唱片公司一直在巩固\N{\fs30}The record companies keep consolidating
Dialogue: 0,1:14:53.99,1:14:56.10,Artifact,,0,0,0,,于是很多都优胜劣汰掉了\N{\fs30}and so, there's less of them
Dialogue: 0,1:14:56.10,1:14:58.22,Artifact,,0,0,0,,当然这主要是因为\N{\fs30}and that's dictated by the fact
Dialogue: 0,1:14:58.22,1:14:59.99,Artifact,,0,0,0,,这是一个行业 而随着行业萎缩\N{\fs30}that it is a business and as business shrinks
Dialogue: 0,1:14:59.99,1:15:01.52,Artifact,,0,0,0,,越来越少的人购买音乐\N{\fs30}and there is less people buying music.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:01.52,1:15:02.97,Artifact,,0,0,0,,唱片公司能怎么办?\N{\fs30}What do the record companies do?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:02.97,1:15:05.98,Artifact,,0,0,0,,他们削减成本 于是结果就是\N{\fs30}They cut cost. So, as a result of that
Dialogue: 0,1:15:05.98,1:15:07.68,Artifact,,0,0,0,,艺人们能去的地方就少了\N{\fs30}you have less places for artists to go,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.68,1:15:09.08,Artifact,,0,0,0,,能签约的艺人更少了\N{\fs30}less people getting signed.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:09.35,1:15:10.50,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我觉得永远不会停止...\N{\fs30}I don't think it ever ends...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:11.42,1:15:12.45,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我觉得永远不会停止\N{\fs30}I don't think it ever ends.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:12.45,1:15:14.11,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我做这一行19年了\N{\fs30}I've been in this business 19 years
Dialogue: 0,1:15:14.11,1:15:15.97,Artifact,,0,0,0,,从我入行时就是\N{\fs30}and it was going on, the day I started
Dialogue: 0,1:15:15.97,1:15:18.36,Artifact,,0,0,0,,到现在一直是 你懂的\N{\fs30}and it's going on now, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:18.88,1:15:21.11,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我不知道艺术和商业\N{\fs30}I don't know that art and commerce
Dialogue: 0,1:15:21.11,1:15:23.92,Artifact,,0,0,0,,是否能美满地联姻\N{\fs30}ever get married like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:30.56,1:15:33.77,地名,,0,0,0,,{\pos(854,596)}诉讼第143天
Dialogue: 0,1:15:36.14,1:15:36.67,Artifact,,0,0,0,,喂\N{\fs30}Hello
Dialogue: 0,1:15:39.25,1:15:40.48,Artifact,,0,0,0,,Jared, Irving要跟你说话\N{\fs30}Jared they're grabbing Irving
Dialogue: 0,1:15:45.28,1:15:49.28,注人名,,0,0,0,,{\pos(470,598)}乐队经理人
Dialogue: 0,1:15:46.00,1:15:47.17,Artifact,,0,0,0,,没人告诉我们 他们要怎样\N{\fs30}Nobody told us what they were gonna do.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:47.17,1:15:48.50,Artifact,,0,0,0,,他们不见我们\N{\fs30}They wouldn't meet with us.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:48.50,1:15:51.16,Artifact,,0,0,0,,他们不喜欢我们!\N{\fs30}They don't like us!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:53.12,1:15:56.28,Artifact,,0,0,0,,嗯 我现在也有点不太喜欢他们了呢\N{\fs30}Yeah, I'm beginning not to like them very much either.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:56.69,1:15:58.27,Artifact,,0,0,0,,纪录片改变了你自己的音乐?\N{\fs30}Documentary changes your own music?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:59.13,1:16:01.13,Artifact,,0,0,0,,嗯 我现在也不太明白\N{\fs30}Yeah, I don't understand how
Dialogue: 0,1:16:01.13,1:16:02.08,Artifact,,0,0,0,,怎么就发生了\N{\fs30}that even happened.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.13,1:16:05.61,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我都不知道我们为什么提这个\N{\fs30}I don't even know why we brought this up.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:05.61,1:16:07.33,Artifact,,0,0,0,,早知道就不提纪录片的事了\N{\fs30}We shouldn't have never even brought it up.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:07.50,1:16:09.50,Artifact,,0,0,0,,不 我是说 他们怎么也会反对\N{\fs30}No, I mean he would have say "no" later,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:09.50,1:16:10.46,Artifact,,0,0,0,,你早晚也得提\N{\fs30}you had to bring it up.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:12.59,1:16:14.14,Artifact,,0,0,0,,你不能就这样把音乐加进去...\N{\fs30}You couldn't have just put the music in...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:14.14,1:16:15.81,Artifact,,0,0,0,,你得说... 明白我的意思吗?\N{\fs30}You had to say... You know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:16.25,1:16:18.50,Artifact,,0,0,0,,就是说 如果有一幕是\N{\fs30}So, if there is a shot of me sitting
Dialogue: 0,1:16:18.50,1:16:20.13,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我在房子里 坐在钢琴前\N{\fs30}and playing one of my songs
Dialogue: 0,1:16:20.13,1:16:22.94,Artifact,,0,0,0,,弹着我的一首歌\N{\fs30}on the piano, at the house,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:23.19,1:16:25.08,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我还得征求EMI的允许\N{\fs30}I'll have to get permission from EMI
Dialogue: 0,1:16:25.08,1:16:26.63,Artifact,,0,0,0,,才能发布这个纪录片?\N{\fs30}in order to release this documentary?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:27.39,1:16:29.31,Artifact,,0,0,0,,没错 他们差不多就会那么说\N{\fs30}Correct. They're  basically gonna say that
Dialogue: 0,1:16:31.75,1:16:33.31,Artifact,,0,0,0,,根据合同 咱们还要再做2张专辑\N{\fs30}we have a contract ready for 2 more albums,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.31,1:16:35.61,Artifact,,0,0,0,,所以这是合同的规定\N{\fs30}so this is a settlement of that contract
Dialogue: 0,1:16:35.61,1:16:37.11,Artifact,,0,0,0,,而根据那个旧合同\N{\fs30}and under that old contract
Dialogue: 0,1:16:37.11,1:16:38.71,Artifact,,0,0,0,,你不能在DVD里放进任何不加他们版权的音乐\N{\fs30}you couldn't put any music in the DVD without them,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:38.71,1:16:40.55,Artifact,,0,0,0,,拥有音乐的只是他们 不是你\N{\fs30}they own the mere music, not you.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:42.73,1:16:44.04,Artifact,,0,0,0,,还有根据他们说的\N{\fs30}And the way they've worded it,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:44.04,1:16:46.05,Artifact,,0,0,0,,他们是不是还有这纪录片的最终剪辑权?\N{\fs30}did they have like final cut over this thing?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:46.05,1:16:48.43,Artifact,,0,0,0,,他们说: 我们要先看看样片\N{\fs30}They're like: we need to see a copy of it
Dialogue: 0,1:16:49.02,1:16:50.41,Artifact,,0,0,0,,然后咱们再谈\N{\fs30}and then we'll talk about it
Dialogue: 0,1:16:50.41,1:16:52.00,Artifact,,0,0,0,,看给不给你音乐的授权\N{\fs30}if we're gonna license you the music for it,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:52.00,1:16:53.21,Artifact,,0,0,0,,是不是这个意思?\N{\fs30}is that basically how it is?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:53.56,1:16:55.75,Artifact,,0,0,0,,嗯 他们是想让你放弃这片子\N{\fs30}Yeah, they're trying to make you abandon the project.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:56.35,1:16:59.05,Artifact,,0,0,0,,想让我放弃这片子\N{\fs30}Trying to get me abandon the film.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:59.65,1:17:02.52,Artifact,,0,0,0,,是的 那 我接个电话\N{\fs30}Yep. So, let's have a call.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:04.09,1:17:04.69,Artifact,,0,0,0,,好\N{\fs30}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:05.23,1:17:05.64,Artifact,,0,0,0,,拜\N{\fs30}Bye.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:05.64,1:17:06.22,Artifact,,0,0,0,,拜\N{\fs30}Bye.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:10.67,1:17:12.03,Artifact,,0,0,0,,全来了\N{\fs30}It all comes down.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:14.14,1:17:15.83,Artifact,,0,0,0,,所以基本上 就是卖掉纪录片\N{\fs30}So basically, you sell the film
Dialogue: 0,1:17:17.32,1:17:18.19,Artifact,,0,0,0,,来换唱片合约\N{\fs30}for the record deal.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:23.74,1:17:25.29,Artifact,,0,0,0,,要不你就把EMI从片子里删掉\N{\fs30}Or you just take EMI out of the film.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:27.97,1:17:28.72,Artifact,,0,0,0,,因为那样他们就会说:\N{\fs30}Cause then they'll say:
Dialogue: 0,1:17:28.72,1:17:30.16,Artifact,,0,0,0,,"当然好啊 我们让你发"\N{\fs30}"Sure, we'll let you put it out."
Dialogue: 0,1:17:33.58,1:17:36.96,Artifact,,0,0,0,,咋样啊妹子们? 喂?\N{\fs30}What's up girls? Hello?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:35.59,1:17:38.35,注人名,,0,0,0,,{\pos(430,596)}乐队律师
Dialogue: 0,1:17:38.72,1:17:40.85,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我看吧 公司里大概分了这么两派:\N{\fs30}To me, there is quite two factions in this company.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:40.85,1:17:43.05,Artifact,,0,0,0,,一派不想跟你们签约\N{\fs30}There's one that just doesn't want to make a deal with you
Dialogue: 0,1:17:43.05,1:17:45.26,Artifact,,0,0,0,,另一派想跟你们签约\N{\fs30}and there's one that does want to make a deal with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:45.10,1:17:48.31,注人名,,0,0,0,,{\pos(474,594)}乐队经理人
Dialogue: 0,1:17:45.37,1:17:47.59,Artifact,,0,0,0,,说你不能做纪录片,\N{\fs30}It's a further slap in the face to say
Dialogue: 0,1:17:48.13,1:17:49.74,Artifact,,0,0,0,,相当于又是句打脸的话\N{\fs30}you can't do the documentary.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:49.74,1:17:51.79,Artifact,,0,0,0,,它没有商业价值\N{\fs30}It makes no rational financial sense.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:52.26,1:17:53.84,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我想我就回去找他们 说\N{\fs30}I think I go back to them and say,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:54.07,1:17:55.18,Artifact,,0,0,0,,纪录片归我们所有\N{\fs30}we own the documentary
Dialogue: 0,1:17:55.18,1:17:56.67,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我们想怎么拍就怎么拍\N{\fs30}and we can do what we want with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:56.96,1:18:00.10,Artifact,,0,0,0,,你能不能再跟他们说一次 纪录片里的生机\N{\fs30}Could you reiterate that there's more to life out there
Dialogue: 0,1:18:00.10,1:18:03.56,Artifact,,0,0,0,,都比这个摇摇欲坠的公司多得多?\N{\fs30}than a bloated failing corporation?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:06.33,1:18:13.73,Artifact,,0,0,0,,啊 操... 今天真是 今天真是的\N{\fs30}Aaahh Fuck... What a day. What-a-day!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:14.10,1:18:14.89,Artifact,,0,0,0,,还没更糟呢:\N{\fs30}Could have been worse:
Dialogue: 0,1:18:14.89,1:18:16.12,Artifact,,0,0,0,,唱片公司完全可以跟我们说\N{\fs30}the record company could have told us
Dialogue: 0,1:18:16.12,1:18:19.62,Artifact,,0,0,0,,操你们祖宗吧... 哦等等 他们就是这意思\N{\fs30}to go fuck ourselves. Oh wait! They just did.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:32.87,1:18:35.63,Artifact,,0,0,0,,EMI应该觉得丢人\N{\fs30}EMI should be ashamed of themselves.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:35.63,1:18:37.54,Artifact,,0,0,0,,他们今天给我们通知了\N{\fs30}They came back with their offer today.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:37.54,1:18:39.05,Artifact,,0,0,0,,只要我们有新进展\N{\fs30}As soon we're getting somewhere,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:39.27,1:18:42.91,Artifact,,0,0,0,,公司里的一些超级白痴大傻逼\N{\fs30}some giant fucking moron at the company, thinks
Dialogue: 0,1:18:42.91,1:18:44.71,Artifact,,0,0,0,,认为他们就能来控制并拥有它\N{\fs30}they're gonna control and own this.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:44.71,1:18:47.05,Artifact,,0,0,0,,但你猜怎么着? 他们可以来跪舔我!\N{\fs30}But guess what? They can kiss my fucking ass!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:47.63,1:18:49.77,Artifact,,0,0,0,,到此为止了 我们不再合作了\N{\fs30}It's over. We are not doing that.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:49.77,1:18:52.16,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我刚跟Irving谈了 那帮傻逼啊\N{\fs30}Just talked to Irving. Fucking idiots, man.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:52.49,1:18:53.33,Artifact,,0,0,0,,好\N{\fs30}Good.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:53.60,1:18:56.80,Artifact,,0,0,0,,黑心公司的傻逼自恋狂们\N{\fs30}Greedy fucking corporate hubris.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.96,1:19:00.90,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我们提议开个会 是吧\N{\fs30}We suggested a meeting, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:00.90,1:19:02.16,Artifact,,0,0,0,,这样我们就能面对面\N{\fs30}So, we can all sit face to face
Dialogue: 0,1:19:02.16,1:19:04.35,Artifact,,0,0,0,,不至于为这事迷失了\N{\fs30}and not get lost in the deal
Dialogue: 0,1:19:04.35,1:19:05.75,Artifact,,0,0,0,,可以人性地处理问题\N{\fs30}and to be human about things.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:06.70,1:19:09.44,Artifact,,0,0,0,,但他们说不 我就告你一声\N{\fs30}They said no. Just so you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:09.94,1:19:10.98,Artifact,,0,0,0,,他们说不 他们以为\N{\fs30}They said no, they think
Dialogue: 0,1:19:10.98,1:19:13.86,Artifact,,0,0,0,,他们可以跟我共同拥有那段音乐\N{\fs30}they're gonna own that piece of music with me
Dialogue: 0,1:19:13.86,1:19:16.97,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我只能在钢琴前装装样子\N{\fs30}just diddling on the piano.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:17.75,1:19:19.17,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我现在就装给你们看 玩玩呗\N{\fs30}I'll do it right now just for fun.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:32.67,1:19:34.40,Artifact,,0,0,0,,那才不是你们的呢 不是我的\N{\fs30}That's not yours, not mine.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:35.69,1:19:37.64,Artifact,,0,0,0,,不 真是搞笑\N{\fs30}No, it's just ludicrous.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:38.98,1:19:41.60,Artifact,,0,0,0,,卖录制好的音乐 那才叫唱片\N{\fs30}Selling recorded music that's the record.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:42.40,1:19:44.39,Artifact,,0,0,0,,在过去 那是唱片公司\N{\fs30}And that's historically the only thing
Dialogue: 0,1:19:44.39,1:19:46.04,Artifact,,0,0,0,,唯一在乎的\N{\fs30}that a record label records cared about.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:46.64,1:19:48.15,Artifact,,0,0,0,,直到现在那不再赚钱了\N{\fs30}Until that's stopped making money.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:48.43,1:19:50.10,Artifact,,0,0,0,,如果30STM今天才起步\N{\fs30}If Thirty Seconds to Mars started today,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:50.22,1:19:51.64,Artifact,,0,0,0,,他们甚至只能签个比他们以前\N{\fs30}they'd have an even worse deal
Dialogue: 0,1:19:51.64,1:19:52.60,Artifact,,0,0,0,,更差的合约\N{\fs30}than they originally signed
Dialogue: 0,1:19:52.60,1:19:54.69,Artifact,,0,0,0,,因为签的是所谓的360合约\N{\fs30}cause they'd have what they called the 360 deal,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:54.69,1:19:56.79,Artifact,,0,0,0,,他们得在他们的销售量\N{\fs30}they'd have to give away a piece of their merchandising
Dialogue: 0,1:19:56.79,1:19:59.02,Artifact,,0,0,0,,和他们的巡演中 都分出一份才能签约\N{\fs30}and their touring, to get their record deal.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:59.57,1:20:01.77,Artifact,,0,0,0,,感谢上帝 我们陷入的不是那样的合约\N{\fs30}Thank god, we didn't get stuck in one of those deals.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:02.11,1:20:05.55,Artifact,,0,0,0,,360合约就是 唱片公司涉入到\N{\fs30}360 deal is when a record label participates
Dialogue: 0,1:20:05.55,1:20:08.46,Artifact,,0,0,0,,艺人所有的收入来源中\N{\fs30}in all revenue streams of an artist.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:09.45,1:20:12.18,Artifact,,0,0,0,,典型的有 巡演 经销\N{\fs30}Typically touring, merchandise,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:12.18,1:20:14.53,Artifact,,0,0,0,,还可能有出版 授权许可\N{\fs30}could be publishing, licensing opportunities,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.53,1:20:15.97,Artifact,,0,0,0,,资质认证\N{\fs30}endorsement opportunities.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:16.50,1:20:18.09,Artifact,,0,0,0,,这是对现实的直接反映:\N{\fs30}It's a direct response to the fact
Dialogue: 0,1:20:18.09,1:20:20.64,Artifact,,0,0,0,,现在没人能卖掉1000万张专辑了\N{\fs30}that no one is selling 10 Million records anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:20.64,1:20:22.14,Artifact,,0,0,0,,就算你有张热门专辑\N{\fs30}Even when you have a big hit,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:22.55,1:20:24.08,Artifact,,0,0,0,,那也不如过去那样热门\N{\fs30}they're not as big as they used to be.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:24.33,1:20:26.59,Artifact,,0,0,0,,所以 如果你要投资大钱\N{\fs30}So, if you are going to invest big money
Dialogue: 0,1:20:26.59,1:20:28.69,Artifact,,0,0,0,,来捧红一个艺人\N{\fs30}in making an artist famous
Dialogue: 0,1:20:28.97,1:20:31.21,Artifact,,0,0,0,,那你就得多找点圈钱途径了\N{\fs30}then, you've got to find more ways to collect.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:32.12,1:20:34.82,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我处理这样合约时 与他们有过这样一段对话:\N{\fs30}The argument I had on one of these deals is they said:
Dialogue: 0,1:20:34.82,1:20:39.82,Artifact,,0,0,0,,-"好 如果我的委托方有了孩子 并出售了孩子的照片,"\N{\fs30}"- Okay, if my client has a baby and sells baby pictures,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:39.82,1:20:42.11,Artifact,,0,0,0,,"你们要从中分钱吗?"    "那当然了"\N{\fs30}do you participate in that? - Well yes."
Dialogue: 0,1:20:42.53,1:20:43.84,Artifact,,0,0,0,,在过去的一年半里\N{\fs30}Over the last 18 months,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:43.90,1:20:48.41,注次级人名,,0,0,0,,{\pos(74,586)}前EMI首席执行官
Dialogue: 0,1:20:44.54,1:20:47.12,Artifact,,0,0,0,,EMI签署的\N{\fs30}90% of the deals that have been,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:47.12,1:20:48.20,Artifact,,0,0,0,,90%的合约\N{\fs30}you know, signed by EMI,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:48.20,1:20:51.40,Artifact,,0,0,0,,都增加了关于权利的条款\N{\fs30}have an extended amount of rights,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:51.40,1:20:54.98,Artifact,,0,0,0,,那就算不是360 你懂的 也是280了...\N{\fs30}if they are not 360, they're, you know, 280...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:54.98,1:20:56.94,Artifact,,0,0,0,,或是什么 之类的 你懂的\N{\fs30}or something... Whatever... You know.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:56.94,1:20:59.61,Artifact,,0,0,0,,所以是的 没错 绝对更多了\N{\fs30}So yes, definitely, definitely more.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:59.84,1:21:01.66,Artifact,,0,0,0,,现在只要是唱片公司都想签360的合约\N{\fs30}Everyone wants 360 now as far as labels.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.49,1:21:03.35,Artifact,,0,0,0,,起码大厂牌公司是这样\N{\fs30}Majors at least.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:03.85,1:21:06.73,Artifact,,0,0,0,,独立公司还没完全到360的地步 你懂的\N{\fs30}Indies are still not necessarily all 360, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:06.73,1:21:07.90,Artifact,,0,0,0,,有的是 有的不是\N{\fs30}Some do some don't.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:07.90,1:21:09.14,Artifact,,0,0,0,,那这对艺人有什么好处呢?\N{\fs30}So, how does it help an artist?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:09.14,1:21:11.30,Artifact,,0,0,0,,嗯 没好处\N{\fs30}Well, it doesn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:11.30,1:21:12.28,Artifact,,0,0,0,,你得不到任何好处\N{\fs30}You've got no leverage,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:12.28,1:21:13.59,Artifact,,0,0,0,,你只是个新人乐队\N{\fs30}you're a band just starting out
Dialogue: 0,1:21:13.59,1:21:17.09,Artifact,,0,0,0,,不管是大厂牌还是小厂牌都不愿妥协\N{\fs30}and neither a label will take this off the table,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:17.09,1:21:18.39,Artifact,,0,0,0,,那么 你怎么做呢?\N{\fs30}so, so what do you do?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:18.39,1:21:20.48,Artifact,,0,0,0,,对于签了360合约的乐队 嗯\N{\fs30}For a band to do a 360 deal, well,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:20.48,1:21:24.52,Artifact,,0,0,0,,现在他们要把真正的财路都拱手送人了\N{\fs30}now, they're turning over their real cash prize.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:24.52,1:21:27.42,Artifact,,0,0,0,,就是他们巡演所挣的钱\N{\fs30}Which is their ability to make money touring
Dialogue: 0,1:21:27.42,1:21:29.01,Artifact,,0,0,0,,以及巡演时销售的唱片钱\N{\fs30}and make money in selling merchandise.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:29.33,1:21:32.45,Artifact,,0,0,0,,唱片公司在360中 一般是怎么分成呢?\N{\fs30}What do labels typically take from a 360?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:32.45,1:21:33.99,Artifact,,0,0,0,,你知道 这要看...\N{\fs30}You know, they vary depending on...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:33.99,1:21:38.21,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我见过从艺人作品中抽取10%到25%的都有\N{\fs30}I've seen as much as 10 to 25% of the artist's piece.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:39.31,1:21:41.76,Artifact,,0,0,0,,你知道 我还见过有些电视明星\N{\fs30}You know, I've seen some of the television
Dialogue: 0,1:21:41.76,1:21:47.94,Artifact,,0,0,0,,公司抽成甚至高达50% 够疯狂的\N{\fs30}star deals go as high as 50%. Pretty crazy.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:47.94,1:21:50.14,Artifact,,0,0,0,,他们完全抱着这么一种殖民的心态\N{\fs30}They've just got this entire plantation mentality,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:50.14,1:21:52.66,Artifact,,0,0,0,,无论艺人做什么事 钱都应该是他们的\N{\fs30}they should own everything that an artist does
Dialogue: 0,1:21:52.66,1:21:56.39,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我从来都看不惯他们那样\N{\fs30}and I've never been comfortable with that.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:56.39,1:21:57.88,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我真是讨厌那样\N{\fs30}I just really hate that.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:57.88,1:22:00.86,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我上个电影 或是电视节目\N{\fs30}I don't need your permission as a record company owner
Dialogue: 0,1:22:00.86,1:22:04.71,Artifact,,0,0,0,,又不用你唱片公司老总的准许\N{\fs30}to go do, you know, things like movies or TV shows.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:04.71,1:22:05.98,Artifact,,0,0,0,,去你们的吧\N{\fs30}Screw you guys!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:21.52,1:23:23.26,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我们拒绝了他们的最终条款后\N{\fs30}After we rejected their last offer,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:23.52,1:23:26.11,Artifact,,0,0,0,,EMI终于同意跟我们坐下来面谈了\N{\fs30}EMI finally agreed to sit down face to face
Dialogue: 0,1:23:26.57,1:23:28.39,Artifact,,0,0,0,,这样我们可以达成些进展\N{\fs30}so, that we could try to work something out.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:29.93,1:23:32.86,Artifact,,0,0,0,,于是我坐飞机去了纽约\N{\fs30}So, I got on a plane and headed to New York.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:37.63,1:23:39.77,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我们已经僵持很久了\N{\fs30}We've been fighting for a long time already
Dialogue: 0,1:23:39.77,1:23:41.98,Artifact,,0,0,0,,所以我们和唱片公司一直都\N{\fs30}and there wasn't a lot of communication going on
Dialogue: 0,1:23:41.98,1:23:43.65,Artifact,,0,0,0,,没怎么直接联系过\N{\fs30}with us and the label directly.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:45.23,1:23:46.23,Artifact,,0,0,0,,其实根本就没联系过\N{\fs30}Let's say virtually none.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:50.16,1:23:50.96,Artifact,,0,0,0,,外面冷死啦!\N{\fs30}It's freezing out!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:57.10,1:23:59.16,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我从小就喜欢这个城市\N{\fs30}I always loved this city ever since I was a kid,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:00.03,1:24:02.68,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我觉得这地方充满魔力\N{\fs30}it's been a magical place for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:02.88,1:24:04.77,Artifact,,0,0,0,,每次来到纽约 我都好兴奋\N{\fs30}Every time I come to New York, I'm excited.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:08.52,1:24:10.30,Artifact,,0,0,0,,很奇怪 感觉这就是我的家一样\N{\fs30}I feel like this is my city in a weird way.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:11.13,1:24:13.77,Artifact,,0,0,0,,比洛杉矶更像家 纽约有某种感觉\N{\fs30}More than LA is. There's something about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:15.08,1:24:16.34,Artifact,,0,0,0,,总有惊喜在里面\N{\fs30}Always an adventure.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:17.84,1:24:19.39,Artifact,,0,0,0,,等等 等等 你演过个电影 我知道你!\N{\fs30}Wait, wait, you're in a movie. I know you.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:19.42,1:24:20.47,Artifact,,0,0,0,,你是个名人 是吧\N{\fs30}You're famous, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:20.47,1:24:21.88,Artifact,,0,0,0,,呃... 嗯 算是吧...\N{\fs30}Erm... Yeah... Kind of...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:22.18,1:24:23.66,Artifact,,0,0,0,,你在那个很酷的电影里    -还行...\N{\fs30}You were in that very cool movie -Sometimes…
Dialogue: 0,1:24:23.66,1:24:25.33,Artifact,,0,0,0,,里边还有个疯老太太\N{\fs30}with the crazy lady.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:25.35,1:24:26.43,Artifact,,0,0,0,,嗯 是的 <梦之安魂曲>\N{\fs30}Yeah, yeah, Requiem for a Dream.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:26.43,1:24:29.52,Artifact,,0,0,0,,哦天啊 哦天啊 哦天 哦天...   -嗨\N{\fs30}Oh my god, oh my god, oh my god... -Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:29.79,1:24:31.08,Artifact,,0,0,0,,你演过我最喜欢的电影...    -你好吗\N{\fs30}You're in my favorite mov…  -How is it going?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:31.10,1:24:32.35,Artifact,,0,0,0,,哦天啊 我要哭了\N{\fs30}Oh my god, I'm gonna cry.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:32.65,1:24:33.90,Artifact,,0,0,0,,你演过世界上我最喜欢的...\N{\fs30}You are in my favorite movie in the whole...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:33.90,1:24:34.67,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我可喜欢那电影了\N{\fs30}I love that movie.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:34.67,1:24:35.32,Artifact,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs30}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.32,1:24:36.34,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我的天 我的天...\N{\fs30}Oh my god, oh my god...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:36.54,1:24:38.03,Artifact,,0,0,0,,你喝的是什么啊?\N{\fs30}What's in that drink?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:38.13,1:24:39.08,Artifact,,0,0,0,,双倍咖啡因吗?\N{\fs30}Extra caffeine?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:40.29,1:24:41.81,Artifact,,0,0,0,,周日是开大会的日子\N{\fs30}It's the big meeting Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:43.09,1:24:44.46,Artifact,,0,0,0,,在纽约感觉很好\N{\fs30}It's was nice to be in New York.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:44.60,1:24:46.25,Artifact,,0,0,0,,终于有机会离开工作室\N{\fs30}I had a chance to get away from the studio
Dialogue: 0,1:24:46.25,1:24:47.65,Artifact,,0,0,0,,来看一些朋友了\N{\fs30}and see some friends.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:47.52,1:24:49.38,注人名,,0,0,0,,{\pos(472,524)}泰利·理查森\N{\fs40\b0}摄影师
Dialogue: 0,1:24:48.46,1:24:50.57,Artifact,,0,0,0,,但这趟旅行的主要焦点还是这次会谈\N{\fs30}But the main focus of the trip was this meeting.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:51.66,1:24:54.04,Artifact,,0,0,0,,想到终于有机会能谈出点成果 我很兴奋\N{\fs30}I was excited that there was a chance to work things out.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:57.50,1:24:58.30,Artifact,,0,0,0,,但很不幸\N{\fs30}Unfortunately...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:00.30,1:25:01.79,Artifact,,0,0,0,,EMI取消了会议\N{\fs30}EMI canceled...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:07.36,1:25:08.90,Artifact,,0,0,0,,要振作起来 还要很久\N{\fs30}It was a long way to go to get stood up,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:08.90,1:25:11.05,Artifact,,0,0,0,,但我在纽约时\N{\fs30}but while I was in New York
Dialogue: 0,1:25:11.15,1:25:16.35,Artifact,,0,0,0,,听说EMI此时又有大动作了\N{\fs30}I heard that there were major changes happening at the label once again and
Dialogue: 0,1:25:16.77,1:25:18.82,Artifact,,0,0,0,,现在跟EMI达成任何约定\N{\fs30}that any possibility of a deal with EMI
Dialogue: 0,1:25:19.74,1:25:21.90,Artifact,,0,0,0,,都是不可能的\N{\fs30}was very unlikely.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:32.71,1:25:34.44,Artifact,,0,0,0,,噢! 我喜欢那个... 他弹什么呢\N{\fs30}Oh! I like that... What he is playing.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:35.83,1:25:37.39,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我去告诉他我喜欢\N{\fs30}Gonna tell them I like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:39.63,1:25:40.44,Artifact,,0,0,0,,你录上那段了吗\N{\fs30}Did you record that?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:41.27,1:25:42.48,Artifact,,0,0,0,,没没 录的是平常的\N{\fs30}No, no, the regular one.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:43.10,1:25:44.27,Artifact,,0,0,0,,啊? 不 我喜欢刚开始那段\N{\fs30}Huh? No, no, I like the beginning
Dialogue: 0,1:25:44.27,1:25:45.67,Artifact,,0,0,0,,你刚才弹的那样\N{\fs30}how you just played that.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:45.69,1:25:46.48,Artifact,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\fs30}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:53.21,1:25:54.76,Artifact,,0,0,0,,它特么的不对劲 因为它变慢了\N{\fs30}It's fucking fucking because it's off.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:55.14,1:25:56.02,Artifact,,0,0,0,,节拍变慢了\N{\fs30}It gets off.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:56.10,1:25:58.11,Artifact,,0,0,0,,你听着节拍就行 你弹的很好\N{\fs30}You just got to listen to the click you're good.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:00.10,1:26:01.15,Artifact,,0,0,0,,等一下\N{\fs30}Hold on a second.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:01.42,1:26:03.31,Artifact,,0,0,0,,好着呢 你跟着节拍弹就行\N{\fs30}It's fine. You just got to keep on that beat.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:03.31,1:26:04.09,Artifact,,0,0,0,,就是节拍的问题\N{\fs30}That's the thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:04.15,1:26:05.81,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我跟着节拍弹呢 但它变慢了    -我知道\N{\fs30}I'm playing to the click but it's going slower.\N{\fs30}-Yeah, I know
Dialogue: 0,1:26:05.81,1:26:06.93,Artifact,,0,0,0,,但你要跟着节拍走\N{\fs30}but you're right with the click
Dialogue: 0,1:26:06.93,1:26:08.01,Artifact,,0,0,0,,所以挺难的\N{\fs30}so it's really hard.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:08.25,1:26:09.35,Artifact,,0,0,0,,你知道 你得像个机器一样\N{\fs30}You know you got to be like a machine.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:09.35,1:26:10.97,Artifact,,0,0,0,,啊... 人类啊\N{\fs30}Ahhhh! Humans!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:14.84,1:26:16.70,Artifact,,0,0,0,,你听出限制器跟节拍不一样了吗?\N{\fs30}You hear that the slicer is not with the click?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:16.70,1:26:17.78,Artifact,,0,0,0,,对吧?\N{\fs30}Right?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:17.78,1:26:18.86,Artifact,,0,0,0,,要不我来弹弹看?\N{\fs30}You want me to play that?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:19.32,1:26:20.93,Artifact,,0,0,0,,嗯 来吧 你弹\N{\fs30}Yeah, go ahead, yeah, please do.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:21.27,1:26:23.08,Artifact,,0,0,0,,给我证明一下限制器是不是变慢了\N{\fs30}Prove me that the slicer is not slowing down!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:24.57,1:26:26.62,Artifact,,0,0,0,,现在就证明给你看 我的拨片呢?\N{\fs30}I'll prove it right now. Where is my goddam pick?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:34.38,1:26:37.69,Artifact,,0,0,0,,就这样 用他的推弦 剩下的用我的\N{\fs30}That's it... Use his pull-off... Use my other thing...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:38.15,1:26:39.66,Artifact,,0,0,0,,这就行了 在两者之间的效果\N{\fs30}It's like the performances between the two
Dialogue: 0,1:26:39.66,1:26:40.53,Artifact,,0,0,0,,就够好了 所以...\N{\fs30}are good enough so...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:41.81,1:26:44.04,Artifact,,0,0,0,,噢耶! 肘子甩起来 亲!\N{\fs30}Oh yeah... The elbow, baby!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:44.56,1:26:45.68,Artifact,,0,0,0,,甩肘子 喔~~\N{\fs30}The fucking elbow! Woo...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:45.96,1:26:48.23,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我们来了傻逼! 耶!\N{\fs30}Here we come motherfucker! Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:48.23,1:26:49.23,Artifact,,0,0,0,,咱们还...\N{\fs30}What else we...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:55.43,1:27:00.22,Artifact,,0,0,0,,你就不想 做出点经久不衰的经典?\N{\fs30}Don't you just want to make something that lives forever?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:00.70,1:27:02.59,Artifact,,0,0,0,,前无古人的 伟大的作品?\N{\fs30}Something that's phenomenal? Something that's great?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:02.69,1:27:04.61,Artifact,,0,0,0,,做出些毋庸置疑的东西?\N{\fs30}Something that's undeniable?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:05.00,1:27:08.11,Artifact,,0,0,0,,能触及到每个人的灵魂的?\N{\fs30}That touches the core of every person that hears it?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:09.00,1:27:09.67,Artifact,,0,0,0,,嗯   -你知道吗\N{\fs30}Yeah!   -You know.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:10.57,1:27:12.16,Artifact,,0,0,0,,嗯 你想做出美好的东西\N{\fs30}Yeah. You want to make something beautiful,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:12.16,1:27:15.35,Artifact,,0,0,0,,感人的 能激起波澜的\N{\fs30}something moving, something provocative,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:15.55,1:27:17.30,Artifact,,0,0,0,,纯净又真实的东西\N{\fs30}something that's pure and true.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:18.58,1:27:19.28,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我们正在做\N{\fs30}We're doing that.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:19.95,1:27:20.51,Artifact,,0,0,0,,但愿吧\N{\fs30}I hope so.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:50.65,1:27:53.28,Artifact,,0,0,0,,从始至终 EMI一直想跟我们重订合约\N{\fs30}All along EMI had been interested in resigning us.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:53.74,1:27:55.48,Artifact,,0,0,0,,可问题是 他们一直给我们的\N{\fs30}The problem was they kept offering us
Dialogue: 0,1:27:55.74,1:27:58.34,Artifact,,0,0,0,,都与原本的渣合约大同小异\N{\fs30}different variations of the same terrible deal.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:59.53,1:28:02.51,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我们决定 愿意与EMI重订合约\N{\fs30}We decided we would consider resigning with EMI
Dialogue: 0,1:28:02.73,1:28:04.58,Artifact,,0,0,0,,只要他们愿意正视这一切\N{\fs30}if they were willing to make things right.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:05.45,1:28:07.01,Artifact,,0,0,0,,尤其是只有这样才能\N{\fs30}Especially as it would put an end
Dialogue: 0,1:28:07.01,1:28:08.53,Artifact,,0,0,0,,结束这场野蛮的官司 才能\N{\fs30}to this brutal lawsuit and ensure
Dialogue: 0,1:28:08.53,1:28:10.18,Artifact,,0,0,0,,保证我们的专辑顺利发行\N{\fs30}that our album would see the light a day.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:11.28,1:28:12.84,Artifact,,0,0,0,,所以我们最后又去找了他们一次\N{\fs30}So, we went back to them one last time
Dialogue: 0,1:28:13.32,1:28:14.43,Artifact,,0,0,0,,基本告诉他们:\N{\fs30}and basically told them:
Dialogue: 0,1:28:14.68,1:28:17.48,Artifact,,0,0,0,,"你看 这是我们最终的条款和要求\N{\fs30}"Look, these are our final terms and conditions,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:17.48,1:28:18.56,Artifact,,0,0,0,,"要么签给我们\N{\fs30}either meet them
Dialogue: 0,1:28:18.82,1:28:20.93,Artifact,,0,0,0,,"要么咱就真没什么可谈了"\N{\fs30}or there really isn't anything left to talk about."
Dialogue: 0,1:28:22.37,1:28:25.68,Artifact,,0,0,0,,EMI回应称他们会在24小时之内答复我们\N{\fs30}EMI responded saying they'd get back to us in 24 hours
Dialogue: 0,1:28:25.68,1:28:27.25,Artifact,,0,0,0,,给我们最终的官方答复\N{\fs30}with their official final response.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:28.76,1:28:33.18,地名,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,576)}诉讼第180天
Dialogue: 0,1:28:33.18,1:28:34.81,地名,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,576)}诉讼第182天
Dialogue: 0,1:28:34.81,1:28:36.85,地名,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,576)}诉讼第183天
Dialogue: 0,1:28:36.85,1:28:38.85,地名,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,576)}诉讼第185天
Dialogue: 0,1:28:38.85,1:28:42.11,地名,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,576)}诉讼第188天
Dialogue: 0,1:28:42.11,1:28:43.69,地名,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,576)}诉讼第190天
Dialogue: 0,1:28:43.69,1:28:47.95,地名,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,576)}诉讼第194天
Dialogue: 0,1:28:28.85,1:28:33.17,Artifact,,0,0,0,,有点奇怪 我们还没收到EMI的信\N{\fs30}It's a little weird we haven't heard from EMI.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:33.88,1:28:34.79,Artifact,,0,0,0,,还是没EMI的信\N{\fs30}No word from EMI.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:35.13,1:28:36.66,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我们在等待一个最终答复\N{\fs30}We're waiting for one finale response.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:37.26,1:28:37.91,Artifact,,0,0,0,,啊...\N{\fs30}Aaahh...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:39.37,1:28:42.25,Artifact,,0,0,0,,还是...没有!\N{\fs30}...And... Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:42.66,1:28:43.69,Artifact,,0,0,0,,还是没有EMI的信\N{\fs30}Still no word from EMI.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:44.01,1:28:45.50,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我们明天肯定能收到\N{\fs30}We're gonna hear from them tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:47.37,1:28:48.63,Artifact,,0,0,0,,明天就是了\N{\fs30}Tomorrow is the day.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:51.31,1:28:51.89,Artifact,,0,0,0,,还不赖\N{\fs30}It's not bad.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:54.42,1:28:57.89,Artifact,,0,0,0,,明天 他们又这么告诉我们\N{\fs30}Tomorrow, which is what we've been told again,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:57.89,1:29:02.12,Artifact,,0,0,0,,又一次 又一次 又一次 又一次...\N{\fs30}and again, and again, and again, etc.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:02.67,1:29:04.56,Artifact,,0,0,0,,永远是明天 明天 明天 明天 明天 ...\N{\fs30}That it was tomorrow, tomorrow, tomorrow, tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:04.56,1:29:06.44,Artifact,,0,0,0,,上帝啊!\N{\fs30}Jesus Christ!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:06.94,1:29:08.78,Artifact,,0,0,0,,麻烦谁去叫那破狗把嘴闭上\N{\fs30}Please someone just shut that fucking dog up.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:10.03,1:29:11.17,Artifact,,0,0,0,,也许他也很生气?\N{\fs30}Maybe he's pissed too?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:13.20,1:29:15.54,Artifact,,0,0,0,,EMI告诉他 明天给他狗粮\N{\fs30}EMI told him he's gonna get his dog food tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:16.33,1:29:22.72,Artifact,,0,0,0,,明天咱就有答复了 明天 明天...\N{\fs30}We should have something tomorrow, tomorrow, etc.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:35.25,1:29:36.42,Artifact,,0,0,0,,感觉就像电影里的人 你懂的\N{\fs30}It's like the guy in the movie, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:36.42,1:29:40.06,Artifact,,0,0,0,,明--天--- 真是可笑\N{\fs30}Tooooomorrrrrrow. It's ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:40.00,1:29:44.29,地名,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,576)}诉讼第209天
Dialogue: 0,1:29:56.35,1:29:57.01,Artifact,,0,0,0,,EMI.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:04.99,1:30:05.73,Artifact,,0,0,0,,卧槽\N{\fs30}Holly shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:10.54,1:30:11.46,Artifact,,0,0,0,,EMI投降了\N{\fs30}EMI caved.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:14.43,1:30:18.33,Artifact,,0,0,0,,"我想我们结束了 结 束 了\N{\fs30}"I think we are done, capital D.O.N.E.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:18.33,1:30:20.41,Artifact,,0,0,0,,"要双方都认可 才能发新闻稿\N{\fs30}Press release to be mutually approved
Dialogue: 0,1:30:20.41,1:30:22.32,Artifact,,0,0,0,,"但等签了约那就不是问题了\N{\fs30}but that can happened quickly after signing,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:22.32,1:30:24.68,Artifact,,0,0,0,,"同时请你说服Jared 把他同意的原话发给我们\N{\fs30}meanwhile could you get an approved quote from Jared
Dialogue: 0,1:30:24.68,1:30:25.93,Artifact,,0,0,0,,"然后我们给你发个草案\N{\fs30}and we will send you a draft.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:28.13,1:30:30.68,Artifact,,0,0,0,,"感谢所有人 现在真正的工作开始了"\N{\fs30}Thanks to all, now the real work starts."
Dialogue: 0,1:30:36.14,1:30:37.47,Artifact,,0,0,0,,现在我们得决定\N{\fs30}Now we have to decide.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:20.82,1:31:24.64,Artifact,,0,0,0,,于是Shannon Tomo和我聚在一起商量\N{\fs30}So Shannon, Tomo and I got together and debated,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:25.04,1:31:27.71,Artifact,,0,0,0,,讨论 并作出了决定\N{\fs30}discussed and made a decision.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:29.07,1:31:30.71,Artifact,,0,0,0,,EMI拿着合约 来找我们\N{\fs30}EMI came to us and offered us
Dialogue: 0,1:31:30.81,1:31:32.29,Artifact,,0,0,0,,是我们一直为之争取的合约\N{\fs30}the deal we were fighting for.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:33.04,1:31:33.84,Artifact,,0,0,0,,于是 我们接受了\N{\fs30}So, we accepted.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:42.52,1:31:44.07,Artifact,,0,0,0,,今天真是13号星期五吗?\N{\fs30}Is it really Friday the thirteen?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:45.53,1:31:49.26,Artifact,,0,0,0,,他们也真够勇敢 大胆的 也够愚蠢\N{\fs30}It is pretty brave, bold and stupid of them
Dialogue: 0,1:31:49.26,1:31:54.85,Artifact,,0,0,0,,居然会...跟乐队签合约\N{\fs30}to actually make a deal with a band,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:54.85,1:31:56.85,Artifact,,0,0,0,,即使是我们 连专辑都没听到就签约\N{\fs30}even if it's us, without having heard the record.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:58.16,1:31:59.76,Artifact,,0,0,0,,但同时 他们也知道\N{\fs30}But at the same time, they knew
Dialogue: 0,1:31:59.76,1:32:01.31,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我是无论如何也他妈的不可能\N{\fs30}there's not a chance in a fucking hell
Dialogue: 0,1:32:01.31,1:32:03.25,Artifact,,0,0,0,,给他们做一秒钟的音乐\N{\fs30}I was gonna play them a single second of this record.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:03.25,1:32:08.08,Artifact,,0,0,0,,但这个时候你只能为音乐着想\N{\fs30}You have to do what's best for the music at this point.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:08.39,1:32:12.59,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我觉得现在为了音乐 最好的选择就是与EMI重新签约\N{\fs30}I think what's best for the music is resigning with EMI
Dialogue: 0,1:32:12.67,1:32:13.78,Artifact,,0,0,0,,然后把专辑发出来\N{\fs30}and putting a record out.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:23.74,1:32:24.75,Artifact,,0,0,0,,这张专辑的目标\N{\fs30}Your goal on this album
Dialogue: 0,1:32:24.75,1:32:26.62,Artifact,,0,0,0,,就是让尽可能多的人来买\N{\fs30}is to have many people as possible buy that.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:26.72,1:32:28.17,Artifact,,0,0,0,,你得考虑你的事业\N{\fs30}You have to consider your career.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:28.17,1:32:29.28,Artifact,,0,0,0,,一切都关乎你的事业\N{\fs30}It's all about your career.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:30.17,1:32:31.60,Artifact,,0,0,0,,那 你觉得我们应该怎么做?\N{\fs30}So, what do you think we should do?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:32.16,1:32:33.73,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我觉得你应该签了这个\N{\fs30}I think you should sign this thing,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:33.73,1:32:34.78,Artifact,,0,0,0,,把专辑发了\N{\fs30}get your record out there
Dialogue: 0,1:32:34.79,1:32:36.64,Artifact,,0,0,0,,然后远离法庭 回到工作正轨上\N{\fs30}and get back to your career away from courts.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:37.05,1:32:38.32,Artifact,,0,0,0,,你觉得我们该怎么做\N{\fs30}What do you think we should do?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:39.35,1:32:41.32,Artifact,,0,0,0,,你绝对应该现在就签了这个\N{\fs30}You should absolutely sign this deal right now
Dialogue: 0,1:32:41.32,1:32:43.26,Artifact,,0,0,0,,然后回工作室去 继续工作\N{\fs30}and then go back to the studio and keep working.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:43.40,1:32:43.85,Artifact,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\fs30}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:43.85,1:32:46.80,Artifact,,0,0,0,,真神奇 在我们签约的同时\N{\fs30}It's amazing that at the same time we're trying making a deal,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:46.80,1:32:48.45,Artifact,,0,0,0,,世界也在风起云涌\N{\fs30}the world is falling apart.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:48.49,1:32:50.23,Artifact,,0,0,0,,你看 在过去七八年的时间\N{\fs30}Look, you've got seven or eight years
Dialogue: 0,1:32:50.23,1:32:52.46,Artifact,,0,0,0,,唱片业一直在走向衰败\N{\fs30}of the record business just going straight to the dumper
Dialogue: 0,1:32:52.46,1:32:53.55,Artifact,,0,0,0,,然后 半年多之前\N{\fs30}and then, six great months ago,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:53.55,1:32:56.34,Artifact,,0,0,0,,全世界都跟唱片业一样了\N{\fs30}the rest of the world went with the record business.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:56.44,1:32:58.29,Artifact,,0,0,0,,现在一切都在衰退\N{\fs30}Everything is in the dumper now.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:58.50,1:33:01.35,Artifact,,0,0,0,,那 我怎么没有庆祝胜利的感觉?\N{\fs30}So, why don' I feel like we should be celebrating?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:01.71,1:33:03.32,Artifact,,0,0,0,,因为这是唱片业啊\N{\fs30}Because it's the record business,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:03.42,1:33:04.79,Artifact,,0,0,0,,唱片行业里真是\N{\fs30}there's really nothing to celebrate
Dialogue: 0,1:33:04.79,1:33:05.91,Artifact,,0,0,0,,没什么好庆祝的\N{\fs30}about the record business,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:06.01,1:33:07.65,Artifact,,0,0,0,,因为这是个夕阳产业\N{\fs30}because it's a dying business.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:08.08,1:33:09.72,Artifact,,0,0,0,,尤其在国际层面上\N{\fs30}And especially on an international level
Dialogue: 0,1:33:09.72,1:33:12.44,Artifact,,0,0,0,,你们的唱片要有70%卖到国际市场\N{\fs30}where you guys are gonna sell 70% of your records
Dialogue: 0,1:33:12.44,1:33:14.21,Artifact,,0,0,0,,因为还是海外市场卖的好\N{\fs30}cause more records still sell overseas.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:14.82,1:33:16.68,Artifact,,0,0,0,,你知道 你们能拿到这样的很不错了\N{\fs30}You know, you gotta have one of these, guys.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:16.68,1:33:18.90,Artifact,,0,0,0,,这是你们不打官司能拿到的最好的了\N{\fs30}And this is the one you get without a lawsuit.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:19.60,1:33:21.12,Artifact,,0,0,0,,Jared 你很理想主义\N{\fs30}Jared, you were very idealistic and
Dialogue: 0,1:33:21.12,1:33:23.18,Artifact,,0,0,0,,你想把唱片业的弊端都写下来\N{\fs30}you wanted to write the wrongs of the record business
Dialogue: 0,1:33:23.18,1:33:25.47,Artifact,,0,0,0,,但问题在于\N{\fs30}and you're not gonna have your chance to see it before
Dialogue: 0,1:33:25.88,1:33:28.68,Artifact,,0,0,0,,在它曝出音乐界的腐败\N{\fs30}it shines a light on the corruption of the music business
Dialogue: 0,1:33:28.78,1:33:30.81,Artifact,,0,0,0,,或是搞垮音乐界之前 不过它本来也快垮掉了\N{\fs30}or take it down, but it's going down anyway.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:30.99,1:33:31.80,Artifact,,0,0,0,,你根本就没机会看到它\N{\fs30}That's the problem.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:32.12,1:33:33.77,Artifact,,0,0,0,,有时候真的很难停止斗争    -难多了\N{\fs30}It's hard to stop fighting sometimes.   -Much tougher
Dialogue: 0,1:33:33.77,1:33:34.95,Artifact,,0,0,0,,你怎么停止斗争呢?\N{\fs30}How do you stop fighting?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:34.95,1:33:35.99,Artifact,,0,0,0,,你怎么能呢?\N{\fs30}How can you do that?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:36.18,1:33:37.68,Artifact,,0,0,0,,因为他们都被炒了\N{\fs30}Because they're all fired.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:38.14,1:33:39.96,Artifact,,0,0,0,,这个 我说一句 是一份合同\N{\fs30}This, by the way, is one contract.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:44.85,1:33:48.07,地名,,0,0,0,,{\pos(278,564)}诉讼第211天
Dialogue: 0,1:33:45.05,1:33:46.60,Artifact,,0,0,0,,深呼吸啊哥们\N{\fs30}Take a deep breath, man.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:47.93,1:33:49.64,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我们的协议是我们非常中意的\N{\fs30}The deal that we made was a very favorable one
Dialogue: 0,1:33:49.64,1:33:51.90,Artifact,,0,0,0,,比三十秒上火星以前的好的多得多\N{\fs30}and a much better deal that Thirty Second to Mars had.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:53.10,1:33:54.50,Artifact,,0,0,0,,诉讼是为了达到\N{\fs30}The goal of the litigation is to accomplish
Dialogue: 0,1:33:54.50,1:33:56.63,Artifact,,0,0,0,,你提起诉讼时的目的\N{\fs30}whatever goal you got the litigation for.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:57.34,1:33:59.37,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我觉得艺人们\N{\fs30}I don't think that the court room
Dialogue: 0,1:33:59.37,1:34:01.23,Artifact,,0,0,0,,还是别上法庭的好\N{\fs30}is a really good place for artists to be.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:01.44,1:34:03.21,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我觉得他们最好还是呆在录音室里\N{\fs30}I think they're better off in the studios.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:06.20,1:34:07.46,Artifact,,0,0,0,,真正的战役是 争分夺秒\N{\fs30}The real battle is the clock starts.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:07.96,1:34:09.05,Artifact,,0,0,0,,你们赶紧把专辑做完\N{\fs30}You got to finish the record.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:09.05,1:34:11.65,Artifact,,0,0,0,,嗯... 对\N{\fs30}Mmmm... Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:13.43,1:34:14.90,Artifact,,0,0,0,,工作回到正轨\N{\fs30}Try to get this show on the road.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:16.59,1:34:17.75,Artifact,,0,0,0,,没有借口\N{\fs30}And no excuses.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:20.56,1:34:22.35,Artifact,,0,0,0,,你们把这首歌做完了吗?\N{\fs30}Have you finished with this song yet?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:24.60,1:34:26.34,Artifact,,0,0,0,,于是 与EMI的新合同规定\N{\fs30}So, the new contract with EMI says
Dialogue: 0,1:34:26.65,1:34:28.42,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我们还有三周的时间来完成\N{\fs30}that we have three weeks left to finish.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:29.01,1:34:29.88,Artifact,,0,0,0,,争分夺秒\N{\fs30}The clock is ticking.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:42.26,1:34:43.71,Artifact,,0,0,0,,你们知道有何种方法\N{\fs30}Is there any kind of methodology that you know about
Dialogue: 0,1:34:44.18,1:34:51.53,Artifact,,0,0,0,,可以提高 我们剩下这几天的产量吗?\N{\fs30}to increase the productivity of the remaining days we have here?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:53.65,1:34:55.51,Artifact,,0,0,0,,对了 Guy Hands今天下台了\N{\fs30}So, Guy Hands stepped down today.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:55.61,1:34:56.33,Artifact,,0,0,0,,哦 是吗?\N{\fs30}Oh, did he?!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:56.84,1:34:58.65,Artifact,,0,0,0,,这绝对是又出了幺蛾子\N{\fs30}That definitely means there's some shit shifting
Dialogue: 0,1:34:58.65,1:34:59.63,Artifact,,0,0,0,,又有变化了\N{\fs30}and changing around.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:00.51,1:35:02.60,Artifact,,0,0,0,,重大新闻 花旗集团接管了\N{\fs30}Breaking news, Citigroup taking ownership
Dialogue: 0,1:35:02.60,1:35:04.85,Artifact,,0,0,0,,国际领头的音乐公司\N{\fs30}of one of the world's leading music companies.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:05.81,1:35:10.85,网页,,0,0,0,,{\pos(814,490)}葛涵思的泰丰资本报告\N百代EMI{\c&H3B22A1&}亏损17.6亿美元
Dialogue: 0,1:35:10.85,1:35:14.69,网页,,0,0,0,,{\pos(140,410)}泰丰资本报亏 免除EMI一半债务
Dialogue: 0,1:35:14.69,1:35:16.69,网页,,0,0,0,,{\fs36\pos(694,454)}神奇的痛苦之旅\N{\fs44}花旗集团接管音乐巨头
Dialogue: 0,1:35:17.86,1:35:20.40,网页,,0,0,0,,{\pos(144,468)\c&H3F1B8B&}泰丰资本奋力地掌控EMI...十分丢脸
Dialogue: 0,1:35:20.40,1:35:23.41,网页,,0,0,0,,{\pos(552,346)}葛涵思失去商业嗅觉了吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:35:25.87,1:35:27.45,网页,,0,0,0,,{\pos(578,390)}泰丰资本的葛涵思从EMI辞职
Dialogue: 0,1:35:27.45,1:35:29.58,网页,,0,0,0,,{\pos(146,472)}泰丰资本总裁葛涵思下台
Dialogue: 0,1:35:06.54,1:35:09.70,Artifact,,0,0,0,,泰丰资本的Guy Hands 收购EMI时\N{\fs30}Guys Hands is from Terra Firma, acquired EMI
Dialogue: 0,1:35:09.70,1:35:12.13,Artifact,,0,0,0,,用了高额借贷的方式\N{\fs30}with a lot of debt and the numbers
Dialogue: 0,1:35:12.13,1:35:13.85,Artifact,,0,0,0,,其数目是惊人的\N{\fs30}never made a lot of sense and so
Dialogue: 0,1:35:13.85,1:35:17.80,Artifact,,0,0,0,,现在花旗集团接管了EMI\N{\fs30}here we are with Citigroup taking control of EMI.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:18.50,1:35:20.71,Artifact,,0,0,0,,EMI的业绩下滑和支离破碎\N{\fs30}The decline and demolishment of EMI
Dialogue: 0,1:35:20.91,1:35:25.40,Artifact,,0,0,0,,是21世纪的一大悲哀的失败\N{\fs30}is a sad 21st century story of failure.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:27.87,1:35:29.28,Artifact,,0,0,0,,他经营的是一整个\N{\fs30}He was running a whole company
Dialogue: 0,1:35:29.48,1:35:31.73,Artifact,,0,0,0,,他一点也不了解 完全不会经营的公司\N{\fs30}that categorically he was incapable of running.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:31.96,1:35:34.00,Artifact,,0,0,0,,显然最后它变成了一个大错误\N{\fs30}Obviously it turned out to be a tremendous mistake
Dialogue: 0,1:35:34.28,1:35:35.32,Artifact,,0,0,0,,收购的时机也不对\N{\fs30}bought at the wrong time.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:35.45,1:35:37.46,Artifact,,0,0,0,,他真的相信他能使之改头换面\N{\fs30}He really believed he was gonna transform it
Dialogue: 0,1:35:37.46,1:35:39.78,Artifact,,0,0,0,,然后再卖掉 我认为他不会想到\N{\fs30}and then sell it. I don't think he thought,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:39.78,1:35:41.76,Artifact,,0,0,0,,他会拥有它 然后输掉它\N{\fs30}that he would own it and then, lose it.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:41.80,1:35:47.47,网页,,0,0,0,,{\c&H886347&\pos(530,466)}花旗集团接管EMI 免除其债务
Dialogue: 0,1:35:43.11,1:35:45.85,Artifact,,0,0,0,,EMI现在 就是花旗集团账上的一颗毒瘤\N{\fs30}What EMI now is, it's a bump sitting on Citibank
Dialogue: 0,1:35:45.93,1:35:49.29,Artifact,,0,0,0,,等着被从账目里清除掉\N{\fs30}balance sheet, waiting to be removed from their balance sheet
Dialogue: 0,1:35:49.29,1:35:50.86,Artifact,,0,0,0,,然后被卖给下一个倒霉鬼\N{\fs30}and sold to the next sucker.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:51.06,1:35:54.14,Artifact,,0,0,0,,想把唱片公司扭亏为盈 可没有一招制敌的\N{\fs30}There is no killer app to turn around a record company.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:54.61,1:35:57.76,Artifact,,0,0,0,,得是慢慢地 耐心地处理 需要很长时间\N{\fs30}It has to be done slowly and patiently and it takes time.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:57.86,1:35:59.16,Artifact,,0,0,0,,抛弃艺人需要时间\N{\fs30}It takes time to break artist,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:59.16,1:36:00.17,Artifact,,0,0,0,,签约艺人需要时间\N{\fs30}it takes time to sign artist,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:00.17,1:36:01.82,Artifact,,0,0,0,,找到合适的高管来介入 更需要时间\N{\fs30}and it takes time to get the right executives in.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:01.85,1:36:05.24,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我觉得Guy是... 我不会当他面这么说\N{\fs30}I think that Guy, and I wouldn't say this to his face...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:05.24,1:36:07.48,Artifact,,0,0,0,,嗯... 他是个很精明的人\N{\fs30}Hum... He is a very bright guy
Dialogue: 0,1:36:07.48,1:36:13.23,Artifact,,0,0,0,,只是不幸地 被舆论所误导\N{\fs30}who unfortunately had the popular misimpression
Dialogue: 0,1:36:13.51,1:36:15.93,Artifact,,0,0,0,,以为音乐产业里全是白痴和小偷\N{\fs30}that the music business is populated by idiots and thieves.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:17.57,1:36:18.93,Artifact,,0,0,0,,那些我们不是没有\N{\fs30}We've got our fair share of them,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:18.93,1:36:21.32,Artifact,,0,0,0,,但是行业里也有很多聪明的好人\N{\fs30}but there's a lot smart, good people in the business.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:21.25,1:36:26.72,网页,,0,0,0,,{\pos(544,292)}音乐公司EMI为泰丰资本\N带来17亿英镑资产减值损失\N{\c&H2425BC&}总裁葛涵思创下行业纪录
Dialogue: 0,1:36:22.78,1:36:24.31,Artifact,,0,0,0,,只是因为那家伙是个亿万富翁\N{\fs30}Just because the guy is a billionaire
Dialogue: 0,1:36:24.57,1:36:26.82,Artifact,,0,0,0,,而且他在别的行业里赚了很多钱\N{\fs30}and he's made a bunch of money in other businesses,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:26.92,1:36:28.81,Artifact,,0,0,0,,你知道 我们业内有很多人\N{\fs30}you know... We have a long list of people
Dialogue: 0,1:36:29.11,1:36:32.93,Artifact,,0,0,0,,作为外行人进入音乐界\N{\fs30}from outside the music business that have come
Dialogue: 0,1:36:32.93,1:36:34.92,Artifact,,0,0,0,,最后毁的不成样子\N{\fs30}and entered the business and left it in ruins.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:35.07,1:36:36.62,Artifact,,0,0,0,,而他是他们中间栽得最大的\N{\fs30}And he is the biggest fool of all of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:37.69,1:36:41.90,注人名,,0,0,0,,{\pos(866,460)}葛涵思拒绝了本片的采访
Dialogue: 0,1:36:57.31,1:36:58.26,Artifact,,0,0,0,,知道我怎么想的吗?\N{\fs30}You know what I think?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:58.36,1:36:58.93,Artifact,,0,0,0,,怎么\N{\fs30}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:59.09,1:37:00.91,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我想我们今晚就能做完这首歌\N{\fs30}I think we're gonna finish this song tonight.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:13.17,1:37:14.07,Artifact,,0,0,0,,挺不错\N{\fs30}Pretty good one.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:14.58,1:37:15.84,Artifact,,0,0,0,,就这样吧\N{\fs30}Let's call it finished.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:16.35,1:37:19.41,Artifact,,0,0,0,,喔! 击掌! 耶!\N{\fs30}Woo! High five! Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:19.68,1:37:25.74,Artifact,,0,0,0,,喔 来啊 别让我举着手啊少年们!\N{\fs30}Woo! Come on! Don't leave me hanging, boys!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:55.70,1:37:59.78,Artifact,,0,0,0,,音乐界的未来是未知的\N{\fs30}The future of the music business is unknown.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:02.18,1:38:04.75,Artifact,,0,0,0,,这让一些人兴奋\N{\fs30}That's what makes it exciting to some
Dialogue: 0,1:38:04.75,1:38:07.45,Artifact,,0,0,0,,也让另一些人害怕\N{\fs30}and really scary to others.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:07.55,1:38:09.79,Artifact,,0,0,0,,因为人们可以在自己家里录歌\N{\fs30}Because people can record in their houses
Dialogue: 0,1:38:09.99,1:38:11.39,Artifact,,0,0,0,,然后在一夜间发布出来\N{\fs30}and distribute overnight.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:12.02,1:38:13.97,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我相信音乐可以\N{\fs30}I believe that music can reclaim
Dialogue: 0,1:38:13.97,1:38:16.17,Artifact,,0,0,0,,收复其主流媒体的地位\N{\fs30}its space as the driving medium.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:16.40,1:38:17.84,Artifact,,0,0,0,,总有变化 有发展\N{\fs30}There is change, there's evolution.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:17.84,1:38:20.37,Artifact,,0,0,0,,如果你不跟上变化 你就得死\N{\fs30}If you don't ride the change, you die.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:20.90,1:38:23.49,Artifact,,0,0,0,,Jared总是开玩笑说 等哪天某个孩子写了首歌\N{\fs30}Jared always jokes that some kid is gonna write a song
Dialogue: 0,1:38:23.49,1:38:24.84,Artifact,,0,0,0,,然后他把它做好\N{\fs30}and he's gonna figure it out
Dialogue: 0,1:38:24.84,1:38:26.34,Artifact,,0,0,0,,然后一支单曲就卖掉几百万张\N{\fs30}and is gonna sell hundreds millions copies of a single
Dialogue: 0,1:38:26.34,1:38:28.97,Artifact,,0,0,0,,全靠他自己 然后他会赚个十亿美元\N{\fs30}by himself and he's gonna make a Billion Dollars
Dialogue: 0,1:38:29.89,1:38:31.32,Artifact,,0,0,0,,他会说 "操你们的,\N{\fs30}and he's gonna say: "fuck you,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:31.32,1:38:32.68,Artifact,,0,0,0,,"老子不需要你们(唱片公司)"  然后那时\N{\fs30}I don't need you." And then,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:32.68,1:38:34.17,Artifact,,0,0,0,,就会是新的开始\N{\fs30}that's gonna be the new beginning.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:34.51,1:38:38.51,注次级人名,,0,0,0,,{\pos(780,558)}声破天(知名流媒体音乐服务软件)\N首席执行官 创始人
Dialogue: 0,1:38:34.81,1:38:35.90,Artifact,,0,0,0,,人们现在听的音乐\N{\fs30}People listen to more music now
Dialogue: 0,1:38:35.90,1:38:37.54,Artifact,,0,0,0,,比以前听的多很多\N{\fs30}than ever before, from a bigger
Dialogue: 0,1:38:37.54,1:38:38.67,Artifact,,0,0,0,,听到的艺人也多很多\N{\fs30}diversity of artists.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:38.67,1:38:41.28,Artifact,,0,0,0,,所以我觉得文化上 我们的处境更好了\N{\fs30}So, I think culturally, we are in a much better place.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:41.28,1:38:42.78,Artifact,,0,0,0,,在我看来 我真的认为\N{\fs30}I look at it and I actually think
Dialogue: 0,1:38:42.78,1:38:45.26,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我们算是进入了音乐的黄金时代\N{\fs30}that we are at sort of entering the golden age for music.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:45.47,1:38:48.86,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我每这样想就很高兴 如今的下一代人群\N{\fs30}I love the idea that we may, in this next generation,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:48.86,1:38:53.59,Artifact,,0,0,0,,不再生活在 可能性有限的世界里\N{\fs30}not be living in a world of the possibility of,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:53.59,1:38:55.42,Artifact,,0,0,0,,你懂的 成功标准很高\N{\fs30}you know, being successful is,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:55.64,1:38:58.17,Artifact,,0,0,0,,你不用成为迈克尔杰克逊 麦当娜\N{\fs30}that you have to be Michael Jackson, Madonna,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:58.76,1:39:01.31,Artifact,,0,0,0,,Prince Lady Gaga那样的人 而如今是\N{\fs30}Prince, Lady Gaga but, that actually like:
Dialogue: 0,1:39:01.31,1:39:02.85,Artifact,,0,0,0,,做音乐人的梦想离人们更近了\N{\fs30}the dream of being musician means,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:02.85,1:39:06.51,Artifact,,0,0,0,,你完全可以以之为生 联系大众\N{\fs30}you can just make a living and connect with people
Dialogue: 0,1:39:06.51,1:39:08.85,Artifact,,0,0,0,,专心做你的音乐 不必去找一份你讨厌的工作\N{\fs30}and make your music and not have to have a job you hate.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:08.86,1:39:10.07,Artifact,,0,0,0,,音乐永远不死\N{\fs30}Music will never die.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:10.59,1:39:12.56,Artifact,,0,0,0,,它永远会带动这个行业\N{\fs30}It will always drive industry,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:12.56,1:39:14.52,Artifact,,0,0,0,,会带动创新\N{\fs30}it will always drive innovation,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:14.52,1:39:17.10,Artifact,,0,0,0,,每个人都能得到\N{\fs30}it will be always be available to everyone
Dialogue: 0,1:39:17.38,1:39:19.79,Artifact,,0,0,0,,每个人也都想得到\N{\fs30}and everyone always is going to want it.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:20.45,1:39:22.54,Artifact,,0,0,0,,而评论界怎么说\N{\fs30}It doesn't really matter what the critic says
Dialogue: 0,1:39:22.54,1:39:24.37,Artifact,,0,0,0,,或是当权者怎么说 真不太重要\N{\fs30}or the gatekeeper says,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:24.73,1:39:27.32,Artifact,,0,0,0,,真的 在如今这个时代的音乐界\N{\fs30}really, in this day and age of the music industry,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:27.32,1:39:29.73,Artifact,,0,0,0,,新的当权者 是粉丝们\N{\fs30}the new gatekeepers are the fans.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:30.15,1:39:34.23,Artifact,,0,0,0,,如果你有五百万听众免费下载你的专辑\N{\fs30}If you have 5 Million people downloading your album for free,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:34.85,1:39:37.55,Artifact,,0,0,0,,那你仍然触及了五百万人\N{\fs30}that's still 5 Million people you've touched.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:38.01,1:39:42.45,Artifact,,0,0,0,,我觉得 那就有比钱更贵重的价值\N{\fs30}and has a value to me that's far greater than money.
